%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20started%20wearing%20a%20uniform%20to%20my%20office%20job.%20It%20made%20getting%20dressed%20in%20the%20morning%20effortless.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221112%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20for%20selfie%20at%20mirror%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ca5582237a6a8f0cdac20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22834%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20wearing%20a%20work%20uniform%20made%20her%20style%20more%20intentional.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20used%20to%20think%20uniforms%20were%20restrictive%2C%20but%20repeating%20the%20same%20five%20pieces%20made%20my%20mornings%20easier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWearing%20a%20consistent%20outfit%20formula%20reduced%20decision%20fatigue%20and%20helped%20me%20feel%20more%20confident.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECreating%20a%20work%20uniform%20didn't%20kill%20my%20love%20of%20fashion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-uniform-experiment-ideas-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20uniforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20for%20nurses%2C%20police%20officers%2C%20or%20anyone%20whose%20job%20required%20a%20literal%20dress%20code.%20Not%20someone%20like%20me%2C%20working%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%20Besides%2C%20I%20wore%20a%20uniform%20majority%20of%20my%20school%20years%2C%20so%20the%20idea%20of%20voluntarily%20putting%20myself%20back%20into%20one%20felt%20elementary.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%20after%20all.%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20let%20my%20outfit%20creativity%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-from-home-surviving-return-to-office-mandates-era-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20early%20remote%20days%2C%20my%20%26quot%3Bwork%20wardrobe%26quot%3B%20consisted%20almost%20entirely%20of%20workout%20sets%20and%20oversize%20sweatshirts.%20Getting%20dressed%20became%20optional%2C%20and%20I%20leaned%20all%20the%20way%20in.%20But%20when%20my%20company%20unexpectedly%20announced%20we%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-rto-policy-affecting-relationship-with-partner-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereturning%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20initial%20shock%20was%20quickly%20replaced%20by%20a%20new%2C%20unexpected%20stress%3A%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%20am%20I%20going%20to%20wear%20every%20day%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20closet%20full%20of%20clothes%2C%20yet%20somehow%20nothing%20was%20right.%20Even%20three%20days%20a%20week%20felt%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20outfits%20compared%20to%20my%20previous%20zero.%20And%20unfortunately%2C%20I'm%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20whose%20mood%20is%20directly%20correlated%20to%20what%20I'm%20wearing.%20If%20my%20outfit%20doesn't%20make%20me%20feel%20like%20the%20most%20fashionable%2C%20put-together%20version%20of%20myself%2C%20my%20entire%20day%20is%E2%80%A6.%20dare%20I%20say%2C%20ruined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbb949e1-c30e-4473-a8d0-0526fd8a4c28%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20seek%20out%20a%20work%20uniform%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20tried%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstylists-reveal-mistakes-you-make-when-getting-dressed-every-day-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplanning%20out%20my%20outfits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Every%20Sunday%2C%20I'd%20map%20out%20my%20looks%20for%20the%20week%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20my%20life%20a%20little%20easier.%20Sometimes%20it%20worked.%20Other%20weeks%2C%20I%20got%20lazy%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20I'd%20wake%20up%20and%20hate%20what%20I'd%20planned.%20%3Cem%3EPanic%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20pattern.%20I%20kept%20reaching%20for%20the%20same%20combination%20of%20pieces%20that%20made%20me%20feel%20confident%20and%20comfortable.%20They%20were%20easy%2C%20they%20worked%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20overthink%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20other%20people%20noticed%20too.%20Coworkers%20would%20put%20on%20a%20blazer%20and%20joke%20that%20they're%20%26quot%3Bchanneling%20me.%26quot%3B%20That's%20when%20it%20clicked%3A%20repetition%20isn't%20boring.%20It's%20smart%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20oddly%20enough%2C%20it's%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-asked-chatgpt-to-be-my-personal-stylist-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20style%3C%2Fa%3E%20gets%20defined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22716c8071-e938-4d87-9c14-9fcad25e3c7c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%205%20pieces%20that%20make%20up%20my%20work%20uniform%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fwhere-to-shop-for-womens-workwear-clothes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20uniform%20is%20a%20formula%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20these%20five%20categories%20are%20the%20backbone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20for%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ca7f52237a6a8f0cdac8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20wearing%20the%20same%20outfit%20with%20different%20blazers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlazers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rotate%20through%20several%2C%20but%20the%20concept%20always%20stays%20the%20same.%20A%20blazer%20instantly%20makes%20even%20the%20most%20casual%20outfit%20feel%20intentional.%20It%20solves%20the%20%26quot%3Bcold%20office%2C%20hot%20commute%26quot%3B%20problem%20and%20adds%20polish%20without%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJeans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESame%20cut%2C%20different%20washes.%20When%20you%20find%20a%20pair%20of%20jeans%20that%20truly%20fits%2C%20just%20know%2C%20you%20hit%20the%20jackpot.%20For%20work%2C%20I%20gravitate%20toward%20wide-legs%20because%20they're%20comfortable%20enough%20to%20sit%20all%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilk%20pants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20might%20be%20my%20most%20complimented%20items.%20They're%20beyond%20comfortable%2C%20breathable%2C%20and%20so%20chic.%20When%20I%20want%20to%20feel%20elevated%20without%20feeling%20stiff%2C%20one%20of%20my%20eight%20pairs%20(yes%2C%20eight)%20is%20always%20my%20go-to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPointed-toe%20heels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20feel%20complete%20without%20a%20heel.%20Even%20a%20small%20heel%20changes%20my%20posture%20and%20mindset.%20A%20pointed%20toe%20sharpens%20the%20entire%20look%2C%20especially%20if%20paired%20with%20wide-leg%20pants%20or%20an%20oversize%20blazer.%20On%20extra-cold%20days%2C%20I'll%20swap%20to%20a%20pointed%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20personality%20really%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20watches%2C%20belts%2C%20earrings%2C%20scarves%2C%20brooches.%20These%20are%20the%20details%20people%20remember.%20Get%20creative.%20One%20base%20look%20can%20become%2010%20different%20looks%20with%20the%20right%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20for%20selfie%20outfit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ca8932237a6a8f0cdaca6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20uses%20accessories%20to%20change%20her%20outfits.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f1cf8f7-b587-42f5-8a2c-9b1105a66d25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20change%20the%20top%2C%20not%20the%20formula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20magic%20of%20a%20work%20uniform%20lies%20in%20its%20flexibility.%20The%20base%20stays%20the%20same%20while%20the%20top%20changes%3A%20a%20white%20tee%2C%20a%20sweater%2C%20a%20button-down%2C%20a%20graphic%20tee%2C%20a%20bodysuit.%20I%20still%20get%20to%20play%20with%20color%2C%20texture%2C%20and%20silhouette%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20start%20from%20scratch%20every%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20work%20somewhere%20with%20a%20more%20professional%20dress%20code%2C%20you%20can%20still%20apply%20this%20principle.%20Swap%20an%20oversize%20blazer%20for%20a%20tailored%20jacket.%20Trade%20denim%20for%20nice%20trousers.%20The%20point%20isn't%20copying%20my%20exact%20formula%3B%20it's%20creating%20what%20works%20best%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20work%20uniform%20didn't%20limit%20my%20love%20of%20fashion%3B%20it%20just%20gave%20it%20structure.%20Turns%20out%2C%20wearing%20the%20same%20five%20pieces%20every%20week%20didn't%20make%20getting%20dressed%20boring%3B%20it%20made%20it%20effortless.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20ultimate%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-built-a-work-uniform-and-stopped-overthinking-outfits-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772117519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ca56aefb52c8bd0deb171%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-built-a-work-uniform-and-stopped-overthinking-outfits-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20creating%20a%20work%20uniform%20with%20five%20staple%20pieces%20can%20simplify%20office%20outfits%20and%20eliminate%20daily%20decision%20fatigue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mia%20McManus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-built-a-work-uniform-and-stopped-overthinking-outfits-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20longevity%20researcher%20started%20taking%20testosterone%20in%20his%2050s.%20He%20says%20there%20are%204%20things%20everyone%20should%20know%20before%20considering%20TRT.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22795%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Kaeberlein%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2fc150f42603b0f8e266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Kaeberlein%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Optispan%2C%20shared%20his%20longevity%20habits.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Kaeberlein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMatt%20Kaeberlein%2C%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-why-a-longevity-researcher-takes-rapamycin-for-joint-pain-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20longevity%20researcher%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20CEO%20of%20Optispan%2C%20had%20symptoms%20of%20low%20testosterone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20got%20his%20levels%20tested%20in%20his%2050s%20and%20gradually%20began%20testosterone%20replacement%20therapy%20(TRT).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20everyone%20should%20know%204%20things%20before%20starting%20TRT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20longevity%20researcher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-researcher-matt-kaeberlein-anti-aging-habits-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatt%20Kaeberlein%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20wondering%20if%20he%20had%20low%20testosterone%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20his%20early%2050s%2C%20Kaeberlein%20had%20all%20the%20classic%20symptoms%3A%20low%20energy%2C%20a%20substantial%20drop%20in%20libido%2C%20and%20an%20inability%20to%20change%20his%20body%20composition%2C%20even%20though%20he%20was%20consistently%20strength%20training%20and%20following%20a%20balanced%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20you're%20working%20out%20hard%2C%20you're%20just%20not%20seeing%20loss%20of%20fat%20and%20increase%20in%20muscle%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaeberlein%2C%20now%2055%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaeberlein%20saw%20a%20doctor%20and%20got%20his%20testosterone%20levels%20tested%20that%20year%2C%20but%20it%20took%20more%20testing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20trial-and-error%20with%20medications%20and%20supplements%20%E2%80%94%20for%20him%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20treatment%20plan%20that%20works%20for%20him.%20Now%20the%20CEO%20of%20Optispan%2C%20a%20healthcare%20technology%20company%20focused%20on%20making%20proactive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Flongevity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%20and%20healthcare%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20general%20public%2C%20he%20said%20working%20in%20that%20space%20helped%20him%20navigate%20the%20early%20days%20of%20his%20low%20testosterone%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Testosterone%20vial%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e209450f42603b0f8d5f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaeberlein%20now%20takes%20weekly%20injections%20of%20testosterone.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Kaeberlein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20TRT%20can%20be%20stigmatized%20for%20a%20few%20reasons.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20this%20idea%20that%20being%20natural%20is%20just%20better%2C%20which%20I%20don't%20really%20subscribe%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Based%20on%20his%20own%20research%20and%20experience%2C%20TRT%20can%20be%20almost%20as%20significant%20for%20middle-aged%20people%20as%20eating%20protein-rich%20whole%20foods%20or%20moving%20enough%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20as%20testosterone%20starts%20declining%20for%20most%20people%20in%20their%2030s%2C%20with%20more%20notable%20symptoms%20appearing%20around%20their%2040s%20or%2050s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20also%20being%20massively%20abused%20these%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20with%20men%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s%20flocking%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-men-testosterone-therapy-masculine-ideal-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestosterone%20boosters%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20they%20might%20not%20actually%20need%20them.%20It%20mirrors%20the%20heavy%20steroid%20use%20of%20the%2070s%20through%2090s%2C%20which%20can%20add%20to%20the%20stigma%2C%20Kaeberlein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20demystify%20the%20world%20of%20TRT%2C%20Kaeberlein%20shared%20what%20he%20learned%20from%20his%20own%20experience%20with%20supplementing%20testosterone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba4136cd-db2f-476b-92b8-a698d6e7eaf3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can%20have%20low%20testosterone%20and%20still%20show%20'normal'%20levels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224045%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20in%20doctor's%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2c3e50f42603b0f8e1d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223034%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaeberlein%20recommended%20seeing%20a%20doctor%20who%20has%20familiarity%20with%20TRT.%3Cp%3EMoMo%20Productions%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20first%20suspected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flow-testosterone-levels-higher-risk-of-early-death-study-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20testosterone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kaeberlein%20saw%20his%20primary%20care%20physician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20performed%20a%20common%20blood%20test%20called%20%26quot%3Btotal%20testosterone%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20measures%20all%20of%20the%20body's%20testosterone%20levels%2C%20but%20doesn't%20account%20for%20which%20proteins%20are%20biologically%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20itself%2C%20the%20test%20can%20be%20fairly%20meaningless%2C%20Kaeberlein%20said.%20His%20levels%20were%20%26quot%3Blow-normal%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20in%20the%20lower%2050%25%20of%20the%20reference%20range.%20His%20doctor%20said%20he%20was%20fine%20and%20didn't%20need%20hormone%20replacement%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Kaeberlein%20became%20more%20educated%20in%20the%20healthcare%20space%2C%20he%20learned%20about%20alternative%20testing%20options.%20A%20friend%20of%20his%20who%20was%20experiencing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommon-signs-low-testosterone-according-to-doctors-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimilar%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointed%20Kaeberlein%20to%20an%20online%20company%20where%20consumers%20can%20order%20specialized%20bloodwork%20without%20seeing%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaeberlein%20ordered%20a%20%26quot%3Bfree%20testosterone%26quot%3B%20test%2C%20which%20measures%20more%20specific%20hormones%20connected%20to%20testosterone%20and%20sperm%20production%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20measuring%20his%20total%20testosterone.%20Companies%20like%20Labcorp%20and%20QuestDirect%20offer%20such%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20results%20indicated%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bprimary%20hypogonadism%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20form%20of%20testicular%20failure%20that%20means%20his%20pituitary%20gland%20is%20sending%20the%20signal%20from%20his%20brain%20to%20make%20testosterone%2C%20but%20his%20testes%20aren't%20able%20to%20create%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sought%20out%20a%20new%20doctor%20who%20had%20more%20experience%20with%20testosterone%20therapy%20to%20figure%20out%20his%20treatment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f301a21-b053-4af4-ab7b-80040896b61a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Natural'%20supplements%20probably%20won't%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boron%20and%20DHEA%20supplements%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e1ff450f42603b0f8d5da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20avoid%20testosterone%20injections%2C%20Kaeberlein%20tried%20supplements%20like%20boron%20and%20DHEA.%20They%20didn't%20work%20for%20him.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Kaeberlein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20confirmed%20he%20had%20low%20testosterone%2C%20Kaeberlein%20had%20a%20dilemma%3A%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20inject%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20needle%20phobia%2C%20but%20it%20just%20didn't%20seem%20like%20something%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20looked%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-increase-testosterone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20it%2C%20such%20as%20taking%20supplements%20said%20to%20boost%20testosterone.%20They%20didn't%20work%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20tried%20Jatenzo%2C%20an%20oral%20testosterone%20medication%2C%20which%20did%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20but%20also%20included%20some%20side%20effects%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20his%20doctor%20encouraged%20him%20to%20just%20learn%20how%20to%20inject%20himself.%20Since%20then%2C%20Kaeberlein%20has%20been%20taking%20weekly%20testosterone%20injections%20and%20has%20had%20success%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20a%20long%20time%20to%20get%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20was%20comfortable%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20taking%20testosterone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20still%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20stigma.%20There%20shouldn't%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224140b9bf-7b5e-4e92-9227-fc490fd06cde%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20where%20you%20stand%20on%20having%20kids%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20holding%20child's%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2ef0e8408f6671803ddb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETRT%20makes%20you%20sterile%2C%20and%20even%20going%20off%20it%20doesn't%20guarantee%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20have%20kids.%3Cp%3EAlrphoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20injecting%20a%20synthetic%20testosterone%20hormone%2C%20the%20male%20pituitary%20gland%20receives%20the%20signal%20to%20stop%20producing%20hormones%20responsible%20for%20creating%20sperm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20lead%20to%20infertility%2C%20Kaeberlein%20said.%20While%20it's%20possible%20to%20stop%20TRT%20and%20slowly%20regain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-increase-sperm-count%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esperm%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20can%20take%20months%20or%20even%20a%20few%20years.%20In%20some%20rare%20cases%2C%20it%20never%20fully%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20case%2C%20it%20wasn't%20an%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaeberlein%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20done%20having%20kids.%26quot%3B%20But%20for%20younger%20men%2C%20the%20conversation%20around%20how%20TRT%20affects%20conception%20is%20sometimes%20overlooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274ddbbd3-2a93-425b-bbbf-4916bbe9f129%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETRT%20should%20be%20the%20missing%20piece%20to%20an%20already%20healthy%20lifestyle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20starting%20injections%2C%20Kaeberlein%20has%20felt%20%26quot%3Ban%20amazing%20improvement%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-lost-fat-changed-body-composition-in-1-year-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20composition%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20energy%20and%20libido%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223679%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20using%20row%20machine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2fa950f42603b0f8e260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222759%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20best%20results%2C%20you%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bdialed%20in%26quot%3B%20on%20your%20workout%20routine%20and%20diet%2C%20Kaeberlein%20said.%3Cp%3ECreative%20Credit%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20more%20drastic%20lifestyle%20changes%20around%20the%20time%20he%20started%20injecting%2C%20including%20cutting%20back%20on%20alcohol%20and%20becoming%20more%20regimented%20with%20his%20exercise%20routine.%20He%20believes%20TRT%20helped%20him%20reach%20the%20full%20benefits%20of%20these%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20this%20experience%20where%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20working%20really%20hard%20and%20there's%20just%20one%20piece%20that%20you're%20missing%20in%20the%20puzzle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20also%20underscores%20an%20important%20point%3A%20while%20testosterone%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20can%20increase%20some%20lean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-more-muscle-less-time-pro-tips-top-exercise-scientist-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuscle%20mass%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20strength%20training%2C%20it%20isn't%20a%20magic%20pill%20for%20looking%20and%20feeling%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20men%20are%20looking%20for%20increased%20muscle%20mass%20and%20strength%2C%20testosterone%20alone%20isn't%20going%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20need%20to%20get%20dialed%20in%20on%20exercise%20and%20nutrition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-researcher-tips-starting-testosterone-replacement-therapy-what-to-know-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772117461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699df6a25b1472b7a25c357b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-researcher-tips-starting-testosterone-replacement-t