y%20to%20remain%20the%20stuff%20of%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitrini%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-boom-recession-citrini-research-layoffs-jobs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%202028%20Global%20Intelligence%20Crisis%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Sunday%2C%20examining%20the%20%26quot%3Bconsequences%20of%20abundant%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%20By%20Monday%2C%20the%20grim%20future%20it%20conjured%20up%20had%20sent%20stocks%20tumbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20is%20written%20from%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20June%202028%2C%20detailing%20figures%20such%20as%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20(10.2%25)%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20(down%2038%25%20from%20its%20high%20in%20late%202026).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20our%20AI%20bullishness%20continues%20to%20be%20right...and%20what%20if%20that's%20actually%20bearish%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20says%2C%20warning%20that%20AI%20paying%20off%20for%20markets%20could%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Citadel's%20Frank%20Flight%20suggests%20Wall%20Street's%20reaction%20to%20the%20dystopian%20vision%20in%20the%20note%20was%20way%20overdone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20macro%20strategist%20kicked%20off%20his%20rebuttal%20in%20a%20similarly%20ominous%20tone%2C%20using%20real%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20year%20is%202026.%20The%20unemployment%20rate%20just%20printed%204.28%25%2C%20AI%20capex%20is%202%25%20of%20GDP%20(650bn)%2C%20AI%20adjacent%20commodities%20are%20up%2065%25%20since%20Jan-23%20and%20approximately%202%2C800%20data%20centers%20are%20planned%20for%20construction%20in%20the%20US*.%20In%20spite%20of%20the%20current%20displacement%20narrative%20%E2%80%94%20job%20postings%20for%20software%20engineers%20are%20rising%20rapidly%2C%20up%2011%25%20YoY.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef6412bc-2416-489c-b7db-b7af6c6af031%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20the%20data%20signal%20about%20AI%20displacement%20risks%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20worries%20that%20AI%20will%20disrupt%20companies%20and%20replace%20human%20workers.%20Citadel%20examined%20data%20from%20the%20St.%20Louis%20Federal%20Reserve%20and%20found%20few%20signs%20of%20displacement%20risk%20among%20the%20US%20labor%20force.%20The%20firm%20assessed%20the%20risk%20using%20stats%20on%20daily%20AI%20use%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20data%20seems%20unexpectedly%20stable%20and%20presents%20little%20evidence%20of%20any%20imminent%20displacement%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Flight%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221454%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20shows%20the%20share%20of%20working%20age%20adults%20using%20Gen-AI%20generally%20and%20at%20work%20over%20time.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f512750f42603b0f8e6da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221116%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20use%20among%20working%20Americans%20based%20on%20the%20real%20time%20population%20data%20is%20roughly%20flat%2C%20rather%20than%20showing%20an%20upward%20inflection%20that%20would%20signal%20imminent%20displacement%20risk.%3Cp%3ECitadel%20Securities%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20adoption%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-layoffs-top-takeaways-earnings-bofa-amzn-meta-labor-market-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekey%20talking%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20executives%2C%20but%20there%20aren't%20quite%20as%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-related%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20doomsday%20scenario%20may%20suggest.%20Some%20have%20even%20tied%20job%20cuts%20to%20cost%20reductions%20to%20justify%20funding%20AI%20spending%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20tech%20directly%20replacing%20human%20labor.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cadcbf72-124a-4d9c-8edb-e0be47af3aeb%5C%22%3ESlow%20AI%20adoption%20limits%20labor%20market%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20adoption%20has%20been%20a%20key%20focus%20for%20enterprises%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20early%20adoption%20of%20the%20tech%20is%20expensive%20and%20slow%20going%2C%20Flight%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20AI%20systems%20will%20be%20able%20to%20continuously%20and%20automatically%20improve%20themselves%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20infinite%20compounding%20of%20productivity%20gains.%20The%20reality%20is%20more%20nuanced%20than%20an%20sharp%20linear%20uptick%20marking%20exponential%20productivity%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20risk%20of%20displacement%20falls%20with%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20adoption%2C%20which%20Citadal%20indicated%20is%20a%20major%20component%20of%20AI%20adoption%20that%20investors%20are%20overlooking.%20The%20market%20isn't%20considering%20factors%20like%20integration%20costs%2C%20diminishing%20returns%2C%20and%20regulatory%20costs%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222bcbbf68-ea9d-45a7-92ed-a2c6a074f8b8%5C%22%3ESupply%20constraints%20and%20hefty%20costs%20weigh%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20challenges%20of%20economic%20deployment%2C%20AI%20workloads%20require%20significant%20compute%2C%20which%20is%20in%20relatively%20short%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-chip-shortage-bad-news-smartphone-pc-industry-ai-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChip%20shortages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20slow%20and%20expensive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-stock-blue-owl-capital-data-center-financing-ai-crwv-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20center%20builds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-energy-use-training-human-water-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy%20constraints%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20some%20of%20the%20cases%20where%20AI-driven%20demand%20outpaces%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dynamic%20isn't%20something%20that%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hype-hasnt-changed-work-yet-bosses-employees-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresolve%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20even%20if%20AI%20does%20advance%20to%20the%20point%20of%20being%20able%20to%20replace%20workers%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20constraints%20would%20drive%20up%20costs%20and%20slow%20integration%2C%20making%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20the%20tech%20to%20be%20a%20viable%20replacement%20for%20human%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20dynamic%20contrasts%20sharply%20with%20narratives%20assuming%20frictionless%20replication%20of%20intelligence.%20Even%20if%20algorithms%20improve%20recursively%2C%20economic%20deployment%20remains%20bounded%20by%20physical%20capital%2C%20energy%20availability%2C%20regulatory%20approvals%2C%20and%20organizational%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209fd33f0-0991-4c7a-a70c-0f1dade52a97%5C%22%3EThe%20economics%20of%20a%20not-so-apocalyptic%20AI%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20doomsday%20described%20in%20the%20viral%20Citrini%20post%20would%20be%20a%20productivity%20shock%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20translate%20to%20higher%20output%20and%20increased%20incomes%2C%20both%20seen%20as%20positives%20for%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20outlined%20that%20all%20major%20tech%20advancements%20in%20history%2C%20from%20steam%20power%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20have%20been%20disinflationary%20and%20growth-enhancing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bears%20say%20that%20this%20time%20is%20different%20because%20AI%20threatens%20to%20directly%20replace%20labor%2C%20hitting%20income%20to%20ultimately%20reduce%20consumer%20demand%2C%20but%20an%20economic%20analysis%20of%20the%20dynamics%20paints%20a%20different%20picture.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20companies%20are%20producing%20more%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%2C%20prices%20fall%20and%20margins%20expand%2C%20bolstering%20real%20purchasing%20power%20and%20fueling%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20scenario%20in%20which%20productivity%20surges%20but%20aggregate%20demand%20collapses%20while%20measured%20output%20rises%20violates%20accounting%20identities%2C%26quot%3B%20Flight%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-wall-street-strategist-citrini-research-citadel-securities-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772117384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f6a461fb3fcb426487729%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-wall-street-strategist-citrini-research-citadel-securities-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Citadel%20Securities%20analyst%20Frank%20Flight%20laid%20out%20why%20the%20grim%20vision%20laid%20out%20in%20Citrini%20Research's%20note%20is%20likely%20to%20remain%20the%20stuff%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-wall-street-strategist-citrini-research-citadel-securities-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David%20Ellison%20has%20a%20message%20for%20Paramount%20staffers%3A%20tech%20is%20a%20key%20to%20winning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paramount%20Ellison%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f25cb50f42603b0f8e0f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EParamount%20Skydance%20is%20investing%20in%20tech%20under%20CEO%20David%20Ellison.%3Cp%3EEric%20Thayer%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Kristina%20Bumphrey%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EParamount%20Skydance%20just%20reported%20its%20first%20full%20quarter%20under%20CEO%20David%20Ellison.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20staffers%2C%20Ellison%20highlighted%20Paramount's%20tech%20investments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERead%20Ellison's%20full%20staff%20memo%20about%20the%20company's%20latest%20quarter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-skydance-bari-weiss-media-hollywood-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%20Skydance%20CEO%20David%20Ellison%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20employees%20a%20shoutout%20after%20the%20media%20company%20roughly%20met%20Wall%20Street's%20estimates%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20progress%20we've%20made%20over%20the%20past%206%2B%20months%20%E2%80%94%20from%20advancing%20our%20strategy%20to%20strengthening%20our%20portfolio%20and%20reorganizing%20our%20businesses%20to%20operate%20more%20efficiently%20and%20effectively%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20direct%20reflection%20of%20your%20hard%20work%20and%20commitment%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20staffers%2C%20which%20was%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20turn%20his%20114-year-old%20Hollywood%20studio%20into%20a%20tech-forward%20company%2C%20said%20in%20his%20memo%20that%20Paramount%20is%20focused%20on%20supercharging%20its%20tech%20and%20data%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20in%20today's%20highly%20competitive%20marketplace%2C%20sustainable%20growth%20depends%20not%20only%20on%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%3C%2Fem%3E%20people%20watch%2C%20but%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20overall%20user%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20are%20prioritizing%20investments%20in%20advanced%20technology%20and%20data%20capabilities%20to%20strengthen%20and%20differentiate%20our%20DTC%20