t%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-skydance-revised-wbd-bid-warner-bros-netflix-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuy%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20seems%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-warner-bros-paramount-netflix-bid-david-ellison-bidding-war-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20open%20to%20Ellison's%20advances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20though%20it%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-to-buy-warner-bros-in-82-7-billion-megadeal-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esigned%20deal%20with%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount's%20results%20were%20roughly%20in%20line%20with%20analyst%20expectations%20in%20its%20latest%20quarter%2C%20the%20first%20full%20quarter%20since%20Ellison%20took%20the%20helm%20in%20early%20August.%20As%20expected%2C%20Paramount's%20full-year%20revenue%20shrank%20for%20a%20second%20straight%20year%20to%20%2428.89%20billion%2C%20just%20under%20the%20estimate%20of%20%2428.95%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%2B%20now%20has%2078.9%20million%20paid%20subscribers%2C%20up%20from%2077.9%20million%20last%20quarter%20and%204%25%20higher%20than%20a%20year%20ago.%20Paramount's%20product%20chief%20told%20employees%20that%20its%20flagship%20streamer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fufc-paramount-plus-million-new-subscribers-leaked-subscriber-figures-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadded%20about%201%20million%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20first%20day%20it%20carried%20UFC%20rights%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20Ellison's%20memo%20to%20Paramount%20employees%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3ETeam%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EToday%20we%20held%20our%204th%20quarter%20and%20fiscal%20year-end%20earnings%20call%2C%20where%20we%20reviewed%20our%20performance%20and%20reinforced%20our%20commitment%20to%20executing%20against%20our%20strategy%20and%20roadmap.%20Anchored%20by%20our%20North%20Star%20priorities%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20drive%20measurable%20progress%20across%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20business%20and%20remain%20confident%20that%20we%20are%20on%20the%20right%20path%20to%20deliver%20sustained%2C%20long-term%20value%20for%20our%20shareholders.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20want%20to%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20thank%20all%20of%20you.%20The%20progress%20we've%20made%20over%20the%20past%206%2B%20months%20%E2%80%94%20from%20advancing%20our%20strategy%20to%20strengthening%20our%20portfolio%20and%20reorganizing%20our%20businesses%20to%20operate%20more%20efficiently%20and%20effectively%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20direct%20reflection%20of%20your%20hard%20work%20and%20commitment.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThis%20shared%20commitment%20powers%20our%20primary%20focus%20here%20at%20Paramount%3A%20delivering%20exceptional%20storytelling.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20home%20for%20the%20industry's%20leading%20creative%20talent%2C%20ensuring%20they%20have%20the%20resources%2C%20platform%20and%20reach%20to%20bring%20their%20best%20stories%20to%20the%20broadest%20possible%20audience%20across%20film%2C%20television%20and%20streaming.%20Every%20decision%20we%20make%20%E2%80%94%20from%20capital%20allocation%20to%20operational%20priorities%20%E2%80%94%20is%20in%20service%20of%20this%20objective.%20And%20our%20increased%20investment%20in%20content%20creation%20reflects%20this%20commitment%2C%20with%2011%20films%20and%2011%20series%20greenlit%20since%20August%20and%20more%20to%20come.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20recognize%20that%20in%20today's%20highly%20competitive%20marketplace%2C%20sustainable%20growth%20depends%20not%20only%20on%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%3C%2Fem%3E%20people%20watch%2C%20but%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20overall%20user%20experience.%20That's%20why%20we%20are%20prioritizing%20investments%20in%20advanced%20technology%20and%20data%20capabilities%20to%20strengthen%20and%20differentiate%20our%20DTC%20offering.%20We%20are%20making%20meaningful%20investments%20across%20the%20company%20in%20innovation%20and%20technology%2C%20and%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20sharing%20more%20details%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOne%20of%20our%20greatest%20strengths%20as%20a%20company%20is%20our%20ability%20to%20mobilize%20the%20entire%20ecosystem%20behind%20key%20priorities%20and%20events%20through%20our%20%26quot%3BParamount%20One%26quot%3B%20initiative.%20We%20saw%20this%20clearly%20demonstrated%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20UFC%20on%20Paramount%2B%20in%20January.%20Every%20part%20of%20the%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20from%20CBS%20Sports%20to%20Pluto%2C%20marketing%20to%20ad%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20contributed%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20this%20landmark%20partnership.%20This%20all-hands%20on%20deck%20mentality%20is%20a%20true%20force%20multiplier%20for%20the%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20know%20you've%20put%20the%20same%20firepower%20behind%20%3Cem%3ESurvivor%2050%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20premiering%20tonight%20on%20CBS!%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20encourage%20you%20to%20review%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.paramount.com%2Fstatic-files%2F182a0313-8977-47de-94d1-5dd89edd9f34%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eshareholder%20letter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details%20on%20our%20quarter%20and%20full%20fiscal%20year%202025%20performance.%20A%20replay%20of%20the%20earnings%20call%20will%20be%20available%20shortly%20on%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.paramount.com%2Fquarterly-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvestor%20Relations%20site%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20couldn't%20be%20prouder%20of%20this%20team.%20Keep%20up%20the%20great%20work.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ELet's%20go!%3C%2Fem%3E%3