igcaption%3ENoah%20Fearnley%20and%20Michael%20Bergin.%3Cp%3EFX%3B%20Ron%20Galella%2FRon%20Galella%20Collection%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20episode%2C%20Calvin%20Klein%20is%20facing%20an%20issue%3A%20Their%20latest%20star%2C%20Mark%20Wahlberg%2C%20was%20allegedly%20caught%20being%20homophobic%20to%20a%20member%20of%20Madonna's%20entourage%2C%20and%20his%20face%20was%20plastered%20all%20over%20the%20city.%20(During%20a%201993%20interview%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bostonglobe.com%2Fmetro%2F1993%2F02%2F19%2Ffacing-protest-wahlberg-apologizes-for-racist-action%2FC8QUpxtnexamtLjiSQIWxN%2Fstory.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20Globe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wahlberg%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20hate%20toward%20gays.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBessette%20comes%20to%20the%20rescue%20by%20recommending%20swapping%20Wahlberg%20for%20her%20friend%20(and%20sometimes%20lover)%20Michael%20Bergin%2C%20a%20model%20in%20his%20own%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBergin%20became%20famous%20after%20starring%20in%20his%20own%20underwear%20ad.%20In%202004%2C%20he%20published%20a%20memoir%20about%20his%20relationship%20with%20Bessette%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Other%20Man%3A%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%2C%20Carolyn%20Bessette%2C%20and%20Me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Fearnley's%20first%20major%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20Bessette's%20closest%20friends%20was%20designer%20Gordon%20Henderson%2C%20played%20by%20Omari%20K.%20Chancellor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Omari%20K.%20Chancellor%20and%20Gordon%20Henderson.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699dd683df1f09368aaaa71c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOmari%20K.%20Chancellor%20and%20Gordon%20Henderson.%3Cp%3EFX%3B%20PL%20Gould%2FImages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHenderson%20was%20part%20of%20Bessette's%20extended%20friend%20group%20and%20is%20still%20a%20successful%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%2C%20we'd%20still%20be%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20Henderson%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.townandcountrymag.com%2Fsociety%2Fmoney-and-power%2Fa65298870%2Fcarolyn-bessette-gordon-henderson-friendship-interview-2025%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETown%20and%20Country%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025%2C%20of%20what%20his%20relationship%20would've%20been%20like%20with%20Bessette%20if%20she%20were%20still%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChancellor%20has%20appeared%20in%20a%20few%20things%20over%20the%20years%2C%20perhaps%20most%20prominently%20in%20the%20Zac%20Efron%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Greatest%20Beer%20Run%20Ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20close%20friend%20of%20Bessette's%20was%20designer%20Narciso%20Rodriguez%2C%20played%20by%20Tonatiuh.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tonatiuh%20and%20Narciso%20Rodriguez.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e2e4750f42603b0f8d713%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETonatiuh%20and%20Narciso%20Rodriguez.%3Cp%3EFX%3B%20Rose%20Hartman%2FArchive%20Photos%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERodriguez%20also%20worked%20at%20Calvin%20Klein%20while%20Bessette%20was%20there%2C%20but%20his%20real%20claim%20to%20fame%20was%20designing%20Bessette's%20iconic%20wedding%20dress%2C%20the%20understated%2C%20chic%20slip%20dress%20that%20can%20still%20be%20found%20on%20wedding%20Pinterest%20boards%20the%20world%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20played%20by%20Tonatiuh%2C%20who%20recently%20had%20a%20breakout%20role%20in%20the%20musical%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Kiss%20of%20the%20Spider%20Woman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnnette%20Bening%20is%20in%20one%20memorable%20scene%2C%20as%20played%20by%20Megan%20Channell.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Megan%20Channell%20and%20Annette%20Bening.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699dd5195b1472b7a25c30e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMegan%20Channell%20and%20Annette%20Bening.%3Cp%3EFX%3B%20Vinnie%20Zuffante%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20show%20how%20easily%20Bessette%20could%20connect%20with%20A-listers%20like%20Bening%2C%20there's%20a%20scene%20in%20the%20first%20episode%20where%20the%20%26quot%3B20th%20Century%20Women%26quot%3B%20actor%20comes%20into%20Calvin%20Klein%20for%20a%20fitting%20for%20a%20dress%20to%20wear%20to%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BBugsy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20doesn't%20love%20the%20dress%2C%20it's%20Bessette%20who%20comes%20up%20with%20the%20solution%20of%20adding%20an%20oversize%20blazer%2C%20impressing%20Klein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChannell%20starred%20in%20the%20Prime%20Video%20series%20%26quot%3BHunters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJacqueline%20Kennedy%20Onassis'%20%26quot%3Bcompanion%26quot%3B%20Maurice%20Tempelsman%20is%20played%20by%20Adam%20Grupper.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adam%20Grupper%20and%20Maurice%20Tempelsman.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699dd79cdf1f09368aaaa732%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdam%20Grupper%20and%20Maurice%20Tempelsman.%3Cp%3EFX%3B%20Sonia%20Moskowitz%2FIMAGES%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20not%20know%20that%20for%20the%20last%2015%20or%20so%20years%20of%20her%20life%2C%20Onassis%20Kennedy%20spent%20her%20time%20with%20Tempelsman%2C%20a%20diamond%20magnate%20and%20financier%20born%20in%20Belgium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20%3Cem%3Ealso%3C%2Fem%3E%20not%20know%20that%20he%20was%20legally%20married%20to%20someone%20else%20the%20entire%20time%2C%20even%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2