pack%20lighter%2C%20and%20prioritize%20less-touristed%20attractions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20began%20organizing%20my%2015-day%20vacation%20to%20the%20Dolomites%2C%20I%20didn't%20realize%20how%20time-consuming%20and%20complex%20it%20would%20be%20to%20plan%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20mountain%20range%2C%20which%20spans%20across%20three%20regions%20and%20five%20provinces%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-visiting-italy-winter-worth-it-venice-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enortheastern%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20Dolomites%20are%20popular%20among%20the%20adventurous%20set%2C%20I%20found%20it%20surprisingly%20tough%20to%20locate%20certain%20information%20about%20the%20Alta%20Via%201%20and%20Alta%20Via%202%2C%20the%20two%20multiday%20hikes%20I%20was%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20weeks%20combing%20through%20blogs%2C%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20tourism%20websites%2C%20YouTube%20videos%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falways-pack-a-guidebook-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ephysical%20guidebooks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Looking%20back%2C%20these%20are%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20(and%20most%20avoidable)%20mistakes%20I%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd356510-a085-4a93-b02f-f790e15fd4bd%5C%22%3EI%20prioritized%20tourist%20hot%20spots%20instead%20of%20exploring%20off-the-beaten-path%20sights%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tourists%20on%20crowded%20path%20in%20the%20dolomites%2C%20italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f0d5b50f42603b0f8dde5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22806%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20paths%20along%20popular%20trails%20were%20crowded%20with%20tourists%20by%20the%20time%20I%20showed%20up.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20search%20the%20Dolomites%20online%2C%20you'll%20find%20photos%20of%20some%20of%20its%20most%20iconic%20sights%3A%20Seceda's%20jagged%20pinnacles%2C%20wooden%20row%20boats%20on%20Lago%20di%20Braies%2C%20and%20Tre%20Cime%20di%20Lavaredo's%20dramatic%20peaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20attractions%20are%20beautiful%2C%20the%20crowds%20they%20drew%20during%20my%20trip%20put%20a%20damper%20on%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20preferred%20sights%20like%20the%20Lagazuoi%20Tunnels%2C%20Monte%20Civetta%2C%20and%20Cinque%20Torri%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20less%20touristy%20but%20still%20had%20equally%20showstopping%20views%20and%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20next%20trip%2C%20I'll%20skip%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20paths%20and%20instead%20rely%20on%20blogs%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-using-travel-advisor-group-trip-paris-worth-it-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20familiar%20with%20the%20area%20to%20find%20off-the-beaten-path%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20also%20avoid%20social-media%20recommendations%2C%20as%20most%20of%20the%20videos%20and%20pictures%20I%20found%20on%20my%20feed%20highlighted%20tourist%20hot%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224dd5cc52-dc0c-46a6-b146-66bc7fc52469%5C%22%3EArriving%20too%20late%20to%20popular%20spots%20meant%20getting%20stuck%20in%20crowds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENumerous%20blogs%20I%20read%20before%20my%20trip%20described%20June%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Boffseason%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Dolomites%2C%20noting%20that%20snow%20would%20still%20be%20melting%20from%20the%20mountain%20peaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20mistakenly%20didn't%20think%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20to%20popular%20sights%20early.%20When%20I%20arrived%20at%20Lago%20di%20Braies%20around%2011%20a.m.%2C%20I%20found%20a%20nearly%20full%20parking%20lot%2C%20a%20wraparound%20line%20for%20boat%20rentals%2C%20and%20a%20crowded%20walking%20path%20around%20the%20lake.%20The%20situation%20was%20similar%20when%20I%20visited%20Seceda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20recommend%20going%20to%20the%20Dolomites%20in%20June%20or%20September%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20technically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-shoulder-season-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshoulder%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20July%20and%20August%20are%20even%20busier.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20I%20were%20to%20repeat%20my%20trip%2C%20I'd%20arrive%20at%20popular%20sights%20in%20the%20early%20morning%20or%20evening%20to%20avoid%20peak%20tourist%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ef52a85-b4d7-455e-b61f-8099ba286e0d%5C%22%3EThe%20Alta%20Via%201%20and%202's%20rough%20terrain%20was%20more%20challenging%20than%20I%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Voss%20hiking%20the%20dolomites%20in%20italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f0dd050f42603b0f8ddf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221234%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20trails%20in%20the%20Dolomites%20were%20much%20more%20challenging%20than%20other%20hikes%20I've%20done.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20goal%20of%20my%20Dolomites%20trip%20was%20to%20hike%20parts%20of%20the%20Alta%20Via%201%20and%202%2C%20multiday%20treks%20through%20mountainous%20terrain.%20Rifugi%20(think%3A%20cozy%20huts)%20are%20stationed%20along%20the%20routes%2C%20offering%20backpackers%20a%20place%20to%20eat%20and%20rest%20each%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20seriously%20underestimated%20just%20how%20taxing%20the%20terrain%20would%20be%2C%20even%20for%20someone%20like%20me%20who's%20hiked%20difficult%2C%20multiday%20routes%20in%20California%2C%20Colorado%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-small-city-canadian-island-love-victoria-drawbacks-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVancouver%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Costa%20Rica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20planned%20for%20my%20boyfriend%20and%20me%20to%20do%20roughly%2012%20miles%20on%20our%20second%20day%20hiking%20the%20Alta%20Via%201.%20This%20distance%20isn't%20unheard%20of%2C%20but%20I%20later%20learned%20that%20most%20people%20cap%20their%20daily%20mileage%20at%205%20to%207%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20stopping%20at%20a%20rifugio%20to%20fuel%20up%20for%20the%20last%20half%20of%20our%20hike%2C%20we%20encountered%20loose%20scree%20and%20steep%20slopes%2C%20which%20slowed%20us%20down.%20We%20also%20ran%20out%20of%20water%20with%20about%203%20miles%20left%2C%20had%20blisters%20on%20our%20feet%2C%20and%20were%20completely%20exhausted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20we%20still%20had%20a%20few%20miles%20remaining%20to%20the%20rifugio%20I'd%20put%20a%20nonrefundable%20deposit%20down%20for%20that%20night%2C%20we%20found%20a%20different%20one%20nearby%20and%20booked%20it.%20Pushing%20ourselves%20too%20hard%20ended%20up%20costing%20me%20money%20and%20causing%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20physical%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20to%20do%20it%20again%2C%20I'd%20plan%20on%20hiking%20no%20more%20than%207%20miles%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228641a68e-0764-47e6-b4f3-b3e36762c3d7%5C%22%3EThe%20ski%20lift%20I%20planned%20on%20using%20was%20closed%20during%20the%20summer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20parts%20of%20building%20my%20itinerary%20was%20piecing%20together%20a%20route%20that%20included%20portions%20of%20the%20Alta%20Via%201%20and%202%2C%20which%20are%20both%20over%2070%20miles%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20planned%20to%20take%20a%20ski%20lift%20while%20hiking%20the%20Alta%20Via%202%2C%20but%20when%20I%20reached%20it%2C%20I%20realized%20it%20was%20only%20open%20during%20the%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20I%20had%20cell%20service%20and%20was%20able%20to%20get%20us%20back%20on%20track%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-public-transportation-solo-backpacking-europe-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20public%20transit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20stressful%20(to%20put%20it%20lightly)%2C%20and%20the%20mishap%20cost%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20to%20consult%20with%20the%20local%20tourism%20offices%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20you're%20planning%20to%20hike.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Val%20Gardena%20region%20has%20a%20tourism%20site%20with%20a%20listed%20email%20address%2C%20so%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20ahead%20of%20your%20trip%20and%20ask%20basic%20questions%20to%20ensure%20your%20route%20is%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20tourism%20offices%20aren't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-luxury-travel-agent-plans-vacations-for-billionaires-and-celebrities-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efull-service%20trip%20planners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20can%20be%20a%20helpful%20resource%20for%20confirming%20public%20transit%20routes%2C%20verifying%20ski%20lift%20hours%2C%20or%20sharing%20important%20information%20you%20might've%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd3704b4-20eb-4982-811a-b3e4ede1c22e%5C%22%3EMy%20itinerary%20didn't%20include%20nearly%20enough%20time%20for%20relaxation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dolomites%20are%20a%20playground%20for%20hikers%2C%20mountain%20climbers%2C%20and%20skiers%2C%20but%20they%20also%20offer%20some%20of%20the%20most%20luxurious%20rest%20and%20relaxation%20opportunities%20I've%20ever%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20every%20hotel%20I%20stopped%20at%20had%20spa%20facilities%2C%20like%20pools%20with%20heavenly%20views%2C%20state-of-the-art%20saunas%2C%20and%20steam%20rooms.%20Many%20of%20the%20rifugi%20are%20also%20accessible%20for%20day%20hikers%20and%20offer%20lunch%20or%20a%20cocktail%20with%20breathtaking%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdid-nothing-during-a-recent-vacation-learned-how-to-relax-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eregret%20not%20slowing%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20taking%20a%20day%20or%20two%20to%20indulge%20in%20these%20offerings.%20On%20my%20next%20trip%2C%20I'll%20be%20sure%20to%20pencil%20in%20time%20for%20some%20R%26amp%3BR%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20long%20day%20of%20hiking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236b8fabc-632d-4142-a459-784e20bd0dd6%5C%22%3EI%20overpacked%20for%20my%20multiday%20treks%2C%20leaving%20me%20with%20neck%20and%20shoulder%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Voss%20backpacking%20in%20the%20italian%20dolomites%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f0e59e8408f66718039a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20would've%20stuffed%20less%20in%20my%20backpack%20if%20I%20repeated%20the%20trip.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recommend%20backpackers%20lay%20out%20what%20they're%20planning%20to%20pack%20and%20cut%20it%20in%20half.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20have%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-wish-i-packed-on-first-long-distance-hike-mistakes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enonnegotiable%20hiking%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20CamelBak%2C%20multiple%20portable%20phone%20chargers%2C%20hats%2C%20a%20first%20aid%20kit%2C%20a%20digital%20camera%2C%20extra%20socks%2C%20and%20a%20jacket).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20overpacked%20snacks%20and%20ended%20up%20not%20reaching%20for%20most%20of%20them%20during%20the%20hike.%20Although%20I'm%20glad%20I%20had%20emergency%20food%20in%20case%20I%20got%20lost%2C%20I%20overdid%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20packed%20extra%20toiletries%2C%20but%20should've%20just%20stuck%20to%20basics%20like%20facewash%2C%20moisturizer%2C%20sunscreen%2C%20and%20soap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a59f82fd-2b50-45ef-bc30-eb939ce422db%5C%22%3EWhen%20I%20was%20making%20my%20itinerary%2C%20I%20didn't%20factor%20in%20fuel%20stops%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20might%20expect%2C%20there%20aren't%20many%20gas%20stations%20in%20Italy's%20remote%20mountains.%20However%2C%20I%20failed%20to%20consciously%20factor%20that%20into%20my%20itinerary%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20travel%20companions%20and%20I%20spent%20about%2045%20minutes%20on%20a%20steep%2C%20two-way%20road%20in%20the%20mountains%20hoping%20and%20praying%20that%20our%20car%20wouldn't%20run%20out%20of%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20takeaway%3F%20Plan%20to%20always%20have%20your%20tank%20at%20least%20halfway%20full%20while%20driving%20in%20the%20Dolomites.%20That%20way%2C%20you%20can%20focus%20your%20energy%20on%20the%20unbelievable%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiked-in-europe-mistakes-lessons-italy-dolomites-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772115182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f0b3a50f42603b0f8dda2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiked-in-europe-mistakes-lessons-italy-dolomites-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20planned%20a%20summertime%20trip%20to%20the%20Italian%20Dolomites%20to%20hike%20the%20Alta%20Via%201%20and%202.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20major%20mistakes%20I%20made%20throughout%20my%20vacation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lily%20Voss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiked-in-europe-mistakes-lessons-italy-dolomites-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Texas%20Republican%20says%20H-1B%20visas%20%E2%80%98pervert%20the%20market%E2%80%99%20by%20forcing%20American%20graduates%20with%20high%20debt%20to%20compete%20with%20foreigners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772115039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128