-sized%20basketball%20court%2C%20a%20shark%20tank%2C%20a%2012-seat%20movie%20theater%2C%20and%20a%20two-lane%20bowling%20alley%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20only%20scratches%20the%20home's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20sold%20at%20its%20listing%20price%2C%20the%20mansion%20would%20set%20a%20record%20for%20the%20highest-selling%20house%20in%20Arizona's%20history.%20The%20current%20record%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%2433.5%20million%20sale%20from%202025%20%E2%80%94%20is%20held%20by%20a%20property%20just%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listed%2011-bed%2C%2013-bath%20home%20sits%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-paradise-valley-richest-city-arizona-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParadise%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20desert%20town%20that%20holds%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20wealthiest%20zip%20code%20in%20Arizona.%20Paradise%20Valley%20is%20comprised%20of%20about%2015%20square%20miles%20of%20land%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20town's%20properties%20are%20required%20to%20take%20up%20a%20minimum%20of%20one%20acre%20to%20maintain%20the%20area's%20low%20population%20density.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20of%20the%20mansion%20began%20in%202020%2C%20designed%20by%20the%20owners%20to%20have%20unique%20spaces%20for%20their%20children's%20hobbies.%20Now%2C%20with%20their%20kids%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%20the%20owners%20are%20looking%20to%20downsize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthealtmanbrothersgriggsaz.com%2Flistings%2F7545-n-mockingbird-ln%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elisting%3C%2Fa%3E%20agent%2C%20Scott%20Grigg%20of%20the%20Grigg's%20Group%20Powered%20by%20the%20Altman%20Brothers%2C%20says%20the%20home's%20eccentric%20details%20are%20unusual%20for%20the%20region%20and%20are%20more%20commonly%20found%20at%20properties%20in%20big%20coastal%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20types%20of%20amenity-driven%20estates%20are%20typically%20seen%20in%20Miami%20or%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20but%20to%20have%20something%20like%20this%20here%20in%20Arizona%20is%20unique%2C%26quot%3B%20Grigg%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESee%20inside%20the%20%2440%20million%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20market%20for%20these%20types%20of%20properties%20in%20Arizona%20is%20growing%2C%20the%20home's%20listing%20agent%20says.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225069%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20house's%20sitting%20rooms.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699c7b01efb52c8bd0deaa48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223802%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20house's%20sitting%20rooms.%20High-end%20homes%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20Arizona%2C%20according%20to%20Scott%20Grigg.%3Cp%3EPhil%20Johnson%2FProVisuals%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGrigg%20predicts%20the%20home%20will%20likely%20attract%20an%20out-of-state%20buyer%2C%20perhaps%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparadise-valley-arizona-wealthy-californians-moving-privacy-luxury-lower-taxes-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20Arizona%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20improved%20quality%20of%20life%20or%20lower%20state%20taxes.%20He%20said%20Arizona%20is%20seeing%20an%20influx%20of%20new%20buyers%20from%20the%20nation's%20biggest%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%2440%20million%20gets%20you%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Grigg%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt'll%20get%20you%20a%20house%20on%20the%20beach%20or%20a%20large%20estate%20in%20California%2C%20but%20now%20Arizona%20is%20putting%20itself%20on%20the%20map.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParadise%20Valley%20sits%20right%20next%20to%20the%20city%20of%20Scottsdale%2C%20which%20was%20found%20to%20be%20the%20country's%20fastest-growing%20hub%20for%20millionaires%20in%20a%202025%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.henleyglobal.com%2Fpublications%2Fusa-wealth-report-2025%2Ffastest-growing-wealth-hubs-usa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20a%20residence%20and%20citizenship%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrigg%20added%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20all%20the%20property's%20amenities%20is%20a%20big%20draw%20for%20buyers%20in%20the%20home's%20price%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best%20and%20things%20that%20stand%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Grigg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20property%20is%20split%20into%20a%20main%20residence%20and%20a%20detached%20guest%20house.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20fireplace.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699c7d78efb52c8bd0deaac5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223992%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20property%20features%20a%20main%20residence%20and%20a%20guest%20casita.%3Cp%3EPhil%20Johnson%2FProVisuals%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20is%20just%20over%2023%2C000%20square%20feet%20on%20an%20estate%20spanning%20nearly%202%20%C2%BC%20acres.%20But%20if%20the%20main%20residence's%20five%20guest%20bedrooms%20aren't%20enough%20to%20accommodate%20visitors%2C%20the%20property%20also%20has%20a%20separate%20guest%20casita.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20five%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20kitchen%2C%20and%204%20%C2%BD%20bathrooms.%20Two%20fireplaces%20keep%20the%20guest%20home%20warm%2C%20and%20a%20golf%20putting%20green%20sits%20right%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20kitchen%20in%20the%20main%20residence%20has%20a%20walk-in%20fridge%20and%20freezer.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225323%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20kitchen%20with%20two%20island%20counters.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699c7d392237a6a8f0cda55c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223992%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20has%20a%20dedicated%20meat%20locker.%3Cp%3EPhil%20Johnson%2FProVisuals%20Me