C%20Utah.%20They%20launched%20Farmer%20Protein%2C%20which%20comes%20in%20five%20flavours%2C%20in%20October%202024.%20The%20ad%20appears%20to%20be%20promoting%20the%20existing%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20almost%20two-minute-long%20short%20film%20posted%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20ballerinas%20from%20Ballet%20West%2C%20a%20Salt%20Lake%20City-based%20ballet%20company%2C%20perform%20on%20stage%20while%20Neeleman%20watches.%20As%20the%20camera%20zooms%20out%20on%20Neeleman%2C%20her%20lower%20body%20becomes%20visible%2C%20and%20she%20reveals%20a%20baby%20bump%20underneath%20her%20checkered%20maxi%20dress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeeleman%20is%20a%20Juilliard-trained%20ballerina%20(which%20inspired%20the%20name%20of%20her%20ranch%20and%20social%20media%20handle)%2C%20but%20quit%20professional%20dance%20after%20college%20to%20be%20a%20mom%20and%20homemaker.%20The%20protein%20powder%20ad%20plays%20on%20this%20narrative%2C%20as%20Neeleman%20is%20later%20pictured%2C%20sipping%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20protein%20smoothie%2C%20in%20front%20of%20an%20expansive%2C%20mountainous%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeeleman%20has%20over%2020%20million%20followers%20across%20social%20media%2C%20and%20her%20%26quot%3Btraditional%26quot%3B%20lifestyle%20splits%20opinions.%20Some%20fans%20find%20it%20an%20inspiration%2C%20while%20others%20lament%20what%20they%20see%20as%20her%20abandoning%20her%20dream%20career%20soon%20after%20she%20married%20Daniel%20Neeleman%20in%202011.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20consistently%20disputes%20the%20latter%20narrative%2C%20telling%20Business%20Insider%20in%20October%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20can%20say%20a%20million%20nice%20things%20about%20you%2C%20and%20then%20one%20negative%20thing%2C%20and%20it%20hurts%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20just%20human.%20But%20I%20know%20who%20I%20am%2C%20and%20I%20know%20what%20we're%20doing%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20in%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhannah-neeleman-ballerina-farm-day-in-life-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Neeleman%20also%20discussed%20her%20approach%20to%20parenting%20the%20eight%20kids%20she%20shares%20with%20Daniel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20a%20business%20where%20we%20could%20work%20together%20as%20a%20couple%20and%20involve%20our%20eight%20children.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20put%20them%20in%20day%20care%20or%20leave%20them%20with%20a%20nanny%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20homeschooling%20her%20kids%20and%20encouraging%20them%20to%20get%20involved%20on%20the%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20visuals%20switch%20from%20theatre%20to%20ranch%2C%20Neeleman%20says%20in%20the%20voiceover%3A%20%26quot%3BOn%20this%20stage%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20be%20strong.%20And%20despite%20what%20some%20people%20think%2C%20that%20strength%20never%20leaves%20you.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeeleman%20last%20gave%20birth%20in%20January%202024%20to%20daughter%20Flora%20Jo%20and%20famously%20competed%20in%20an%20international%20beauty%20pageant%2012%20days%20later.%20If%20Farmer%20Protein%20is%20in%20fact%20behind%20this%20woman's%20preternatural%20stamina%2C%20maybe%20we%20really%20should%20all%20be%20taking%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fballerina-farm-announced-her-9th-pregnancy-in-a-protein-ad-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772112615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0489650f42603b0f8f0a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fballerina-farm-announced-her-9th-pregnancy-in-a-protein-ad-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20October%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Hannah%20Neeleman%20discussed%20her%20free-range%20approach%20to%20parenting%20her%20eight%20kids.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%4