%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Cuban%20at%20A24's%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%26quot%3B%20New%20York%20Premiere%20on%20December%2016%2C%202025%20in%20New%20York%2C%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a017ec50f42603b0f8efc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Cuban%20says%20AI%20has%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20any%20curious%20kid%20to%20turn%20one%20idea%20into%20something%20world-changing.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Nacion%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBillionaire%20Mark%20Cuban%20said%20AI%20has%20put%20the%20world's%20knowledge%20at%20any%20curious%20kid's%20fingertips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAll%20it%20takes%20is%20one%20good%20idea%20from%20some%20kid%20everybody%20thought%20was%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20lets%20young%20builders%20teach%20themselves%20and%20move%20from%20idea%20to%20worldwide%20impact%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Cuban%20believes%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%20fundamentally%20changed%20who%20gets%20to%20innovate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-says-ending-billionaires-would-destroy-the-stock-market-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebillionaire%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20former%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20investor%20said%20we've%20entered%20a%20moment%20where%20%26quot%3Bsome%20kid%20in%20a%20basement%26quot%3B%20can%20build%20something%20that%20transforms%20an%20industry%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-human-intelligence-impact-at-work-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20put%20the%20world's%20knowledge%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20it%20takes%20is%20one%20good%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20told%20Eric%20Bricker%2C%20former%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20medical%20officer%20of%20Compass%20Professional%20Health%20Services%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20released%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20not%20you%3F%20Why%20can't%20a%2012-year-old%2C%2014-year-old%2C%2020-year-old%2C%2025-year-old%2C%20whatever%20it%20may%20be%2C%20come%20up%20with%20something%20that%20changes%20the%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20pointed%20to%20AI%20tools%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-ai-tools-tech-selloff-software-apocalypse-cybersecurity-anthropic-ibm-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-personal-intelligence-app-empire-gemini-edge-openai-anthropic-ai-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20turning%20point.%20Just%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20curious%20student%20without%20access%20to%20strong%20teachers%20or%20resources%20might%20have%20struggled%20to%20go%20deep%20on%20a%20topic.%20Now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20they%20can%20create%20their%20own%20curriculum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20curious%20about%20something%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20your%20own%20curriculum%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20said%2C%20describing%20how%20a%20young%20person%20could%20ask%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20teach%20them%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20become%20a%20surgeon%20or%20understand%20robotic%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20you%20are%20unable%20to%20learn%20if%20you%20put%20in%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20that%20AI%20systems%20can%20hallucinate%20but%20said%20that%20access%20to%20instant%20explanations%2C%20iteration%2C%20and%20feedback%20dramatically%20lowers%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20ambitious%20builders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20framed%20the%20shift%20as%20especially%20powerful%20in%20healthcare%2C%20an%20industry%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20disrupt%20through%20ventures%20like%20Cost%20Plus%20Drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20it%20takes%20is%20one%20good%20idea%20from%20some%20kid%20everybody%20thought%20was%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20also%20said%20AI%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20act%20on%20ideas.%20Someone%20who%20wants%20to%20develop%20a%20concept%20or%20even%20file%20a%20patent%20can%20ask%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20me%20write%20this%20patent%20%E2%80%94%20boom%20boom%20boom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20builders%20now%20have%20instant%20access%20to%20knowledge%20that%20once%20required%20expensive%20experts%20or%20years%20in%20a%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Cuban%2C%20the%20opportunity%20is%20less%20about%20hype%20and%20more%20about%20access.%20The%20combination%20of%20AI%20tools%20and%20global%20communication%20platforms%20means%20that%20once%20someone%20builds%20something%20meaningful%2C%20they%20can%20scale%20it%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20that%20can%20stop%20you%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20just%20so%20powerful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-lets-any-kid-build-something-world-changing-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772111939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a01806e8408f6671804b5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-lets-any-kid-build-something-world-changing-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cuban%20says%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20let%20curious%20kids%20teach%20themselves%20and%20turn%20one%20idea%20into%20a%20potentially%20life-changing%20product.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibau