t%20used%20to%20it.%20I%20think%20in%20some%20ways%20it's%20easier%20for%20it%20to%20happen%20when%20you're%20very%20young%20because%20then%20the%20weirdness%20of%20it%20gets%20so%20intertwined%20with%20your%20life%20that%20it%20doesn't%20really%20feel%20weird%20anymore.%20You%20don't%20register%20it%20as%20being%20so%20bizarre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20challenge%20it%20presents%20you%20with%20%E2%80%94%20as%20with%20any%20kind%20of%20fame%20%E2%80%94%20is%20you%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20actually%20makes%20you%20happy%2C%20and%20then%20aim%20for%20that%2C%20and%20nothing%20else%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20people%20around%20me.%20I%20always%20did.%20I%20had%20great%20parents%2C%20but%20also%20all%20the%20other%20adults%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BPotter%26quot%3B%20set.%20I%20did%20get%20some%20really%20good%20advice%20from%20some%20of%20the%20older%20actors%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20great%20advice%20I%20got%20came%20from%20crew%20or%20people%20I%20really%20knew%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20signing%20autographs%20in%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697b618da645d1188188386d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222042%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Radcliffe%20signing%20autographs%20in%20Japan%20in%202007.%3Cp%3EJunko%20Kimura%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20the%20fame%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharry-potter-tv-series-info-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20%5B%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%5D%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20little%20of%20a%20shared%20burden%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20nice.%20There%20are%20now%20multiple%20Harry%20Potters%20in%20the%20world%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20like%20that's%20going%20to%20help.%20And%20there%20will%20be%20a%20time%20when%2C%20I%20feel%20at%20some%20point%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20start%20looking%20less%20like%20Potter%3B%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20old%2C%20and%20that%20will%20probably%20be%20another%20thing%20that%20helps%20in%20recognition%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20fame%20starts%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20you%20start%20getting%20this%20version%20of%20yourself%20reflected%20back%20at%20you%20from%20the%20world%2C%20but%20in%20a%20false%20mirror%20where%20suddenly%20you're%20hearing%20this%20perceived%20version%20of%20yourself.%20You%20have%20to%20figure%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BAm%20I%20that%3F%20Do%20I%20really%20want%20to%20be%20that%3F%20Or%20do%20I%20actually%20want%20to%20be%20something%20else%2C%20and%20what's%20important%20to%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what's%20important%20to%20you%20and%20what%20you%20like.%20And%20I%20was%20really%20lucky%20because%20I%20always%20loved%20being%20on%20set%2C%20so%20I%20just%20needed%20to%20keep%20doing%20this%20in%20some%20form.%20You%20can%20put%20me%20on%20anything%2C%20and%20I'll%20basically%20be%20happy%20if%20I'm%20on%20a%20film%20set.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2240afebd1-3c5c-4697-8891-6e778965d94f%5C%22%3EOn%20playing%20himself%20as%20an%20entitled%20child%20star%20on%20'Extras'%20and%20choosing%20offbeat%20roles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20holding%20onto%20a%20condom%20in%20Extras%20episode%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697b6291d3c7faef0ecd2825%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Radcliffe%20in%20%26quot%3BExtras.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20first%20non-%26quot%3BPotter%26quot%3B%20project%20we%20saw%20you%20in%20was%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiME60JZInfw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%