B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swiss%20Army%20Man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e7b7fbb671de035b957b4ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Scheinert%2FDaniel%20Kwan%3Cp%3EA24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20consistently%20have%20chosen%20offbeat%20roles%20in%20your%20post-%26quot%3BPotter%26quot%3B%20career.%20Did%20that%20happen%20naturally%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah.%20It's%20just%20my%20taste.%20I%20think%20%26quot%3BSwiss%20Army%20Man%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20film%20where%20people%20always%20assumed%20that%20I%20had%20to%20be%20talked%20into%20doing%20it%20because%20it's%20so%20weird.%20In%20reality%2C%20I%20read%20the%20script%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20great%2C%20this%20is%20some%20weird%20fucking%20Beckett%20play%2C%20it's%20fantastic.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20think%20it's%20always%20been%20my%20taste%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20in%20this%20incredible%20position%20where%20I%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20guided%20by%20my%20taste%20and%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20in%20film%2C%20TV%2C%20and%20stage%2C%20if%20you%20are%20in%20a%20place%20where%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20second-guess%20what%20audiences%20want%20or%20what%20people%20want%20to%20see%20you%20in%2C%20that%20will%20always%20lead%20to%20some%20bad%20decisions.%20If%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20something%20you%20don't%20really%20believe%20in%2C%20but%20you%20think%20other%20people%20think%20you%20should%20do%20it%2C%20suddenly%20you're%20in%20a%20position%20where%20the%20only%20way%20it%20can%20be%20a%20success%20is%20if%20it%20makes%20a%20shit%20ton%20of%20money%2C%20which%20almost%20nothing%20does%2C%20or%20it%20is%20incredibly%20well%20reviewed%2C%20which%20might%20happen%20but%20might%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20feel%20like%20if%20you%20do%20something%20because%20you%20love%20it%2C%20then%20it's%20already%20a%20success.%20And%20if%20anything%20else%20happens%20after%20that%2C%20great%2C%20it's%20a%20bonus.%20But%20if%20you%20had%20a%20good%20time%20making%20it%2C%20that's%20really%20all%20that%20counts.%20I'm%20not%20someone%20who%20goes%20back%20and%20watches%20my%20work%20ever%2C%20so%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20to%20me.%20Obviously%2C%20I%20want%20things%20to%20turn%20out%20well%2C%20but%20the%20main%20thing%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20left%20with%20is%20the%20experience%20I%20had%20making%20something.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20got%20to%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaniel-radcliffe-and-paul-dano-interview-on-swiss-army-man-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Espeak%20to%20you%20and%20Paul%20Dano%20for%20%26quot%3BSwiss%20Army%20Man%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20it%20still%20amazes%20me%20that%20it's%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJMBOsy-uZ5g%3Fsi%3DPh3paw4Hsdp9S2Bw%26t%3D130%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ereally%20you%20in%20that%20opening%20scene%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20with%20Paul%20on%20top%20of%20you%20in%20the%20water.%20Were%20you%20just%20game%20to%20do%20whatever%20the%20Daniels%20wanted%20you%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20really%20is%20residual%20left%20over%20from%20%26quot%3BPotter%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20I%20got%20to%20do%20some%20of%20the%20craziest%20stunts%20I%20will%20ever%20get%20to%20do.%20I'm%20more%20physically%20capable%20than%20people%20expect%20me%20to%20be%2C%20so%20I'm%20always%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20throw%20me%20around.%26quot%3B%20So%20as%20soon%20as%20there%20was%20a%20chance%20for%20me%20being%20able%20to%20do%20that%20bit%20myself%20on%20%26quot%3BSwiss%20Army%20Man%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAbsolutely%2C%20I%20will%20want%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%20And%20part%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20that%20film%20was%20I%20don't%20want%20a%20dummy%20to%20play%20this%20role%2C%20I%20want%20it%20to%20be%20me.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ed197d1-3c28-4834-b4da-ad7465aa8e23%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20awkward%20movie%20scene%20he%20doesn't%20want%20his%20son%20to%20see%2C%20and%20the%20best%20career%20decision%20he%20ever%20made%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20and%20Erin%20Darke%20in%20a%20library%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697b6511d3c7faef0ecd284d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Radcliffe%20and%20Erin%20Darke%20in%20%26quot%3BKill%20Your%20Darlings.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESony%20Pictures%20Classics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20thought%20about%20how%20you%20will%20explain%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZOFatKD0Vzo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuns%20Akimbo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20your%20child%20when%20he's%20old%20enough%20to%20understand%20what%20%26quot%3BGuns%20Akimbo%26quot%3B%20is%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUm%2C%20not%20that%20one.%20The%20one%20that%20has%20come%20to%20mind%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4LBtR2zrtCo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKill%20Your%20Darlings%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20because%20that's%20the%20film%20me%20and%20his%20mum%20%5BErin%20Darke%5D%20met%20on.%20And%20it's%20also%20a%20film%20where%20I%20have%20a%20sex%20scene%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20scene%20where%20his%20mum%20gives%20me%20a%20blowjob%20in%20the%20library.%20So%20that's%20the%20film%20where%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAh%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20avoid%20this%20one%20for%20a%20while%2C%20pal.%26quot%3B%20%5B%3Cem%3ELaughs%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3BGuns%20Akimbo%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20time%20he's%20a%20teenager%20and%20ready%20to%20understand%20it%2C%20that's%20probably%20my%20easiest%20sell%20of%20a%20movie%20to%20a%20teenage%20boy.%20That's%20one%20of%20the%20ones%20he%20might%20actually%20enjoy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221941%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22daniel%20radcliffe%20as%20al%20yankovic%20playing%20the%20accordian%20in%20weird%20the%20al%20yonkovic%20story%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697b66c6a645d118818838c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22970%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Radcliffe%20in%20%26quot%3BWeird%3A%20The%20Al%20Yankovic%20Story.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERoku%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202022%2C%20you%20were%20in%20two%20very%20different%20movies%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lost%20City%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWeird%3A%20The%20Al%20Yankovic%20Story.%26quot%3B%20What%20was%20it%20like%20having%20audiences%20see%20you%20in%20these%20roles%20around%20the%20same%20time%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Lost%20City%26quot%3B%20was%20very%2C%20very%20easy.%20It%20was%20a%20lovely%20job%20with%20Channing%20Tatum%20and%20Sandra%20Bullock%2C%20two%20of%20the%20most%20talented%2C%20charming%2C%20charismatic%20actors%2C%20and%20me%20playing%20a%20bad%20guy.%20I%20feel%20I%20play%20one%20type%20of%20bad%20guy%2C%20and%20it%20the%20is%20spoiled%2C%20bratty%20son%20of%20rich%20person.%20It's%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20to%20do%2C%20and%20I%20was%20so%20glad%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20fun%20action%20comedy.%20It%20didn't%20feel%20high%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeird%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20actually%20felt%20tons%20of%20pressure.%20Al%20has%20such%20a%20devoted%20and%20wonderful%20fan%20base%2C%20and%20he%20has%20such%20an%20incredible%20legacy%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20the%20movie%20to%20be%20shit%20and%20me%20to%20be%20shit%20playing%20him.%20So%20I%20was%20really%20relieved%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20truly%20did%20not%20know%20before%20it%20came%20out%20how%20people%20were%20going%20to%20respond%2C%20and%20when%20people%20started%20seeing%20it%20and%20started%20loving%20it%2C%20I%20remember%20being%20so%20relieved.%20I%20loved%20making%20that%20movie.%20I%20shot%20my%20whole%20part%20of%20that%20movie%20in%2014%20days.%20It%20was%20incredibly%20fast.%20The%20stunts%20I%20learned%20on%20%26quot%3BPotter%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20dancing%20I%20learned%20for%20Broadway%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20to%20use%20all%20these%20skills%20I%20had%20learned%20from%20other%20jobs%20on%20this%20movie%20in%20a%20hyper-focused%20way.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20arms%20outreached%20screaming%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697b67f5a645d118818838d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Radcliffe%20performing%20%26quot%3BEquus%26quot%3B%20in%202007.%3Cp%3ERobbie%20Jack%2FCorbis%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20feel%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20best%20business%20decision%20you%20ever%20made%3F%20Being%20paid%20what%20you%20were%20on%20those%20movies%2C%20that%20it%20gave%20you%20the%20freedom%20to%20go%20do%20a%20%26quot%3BSwiss%20Army%20Man%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20%26quot%3BKill%20Your%20Darlings%26quot%3B%20without%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20a%20paycheck%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20absolutely.%20The%20best%20business%20decision%20I%20ever%20made%20is%20suddenly%20realizing%20what%20freedom%20you%20have%20because%20you've%20been%20given%20it%20by%20this%20incredible%20first%20job%3B%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20financial%20security%2C%20but%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20visibility.%20For%20at%20least%20a%20few%20years%2C%20my%20name%20will%20carry%20enough%20cachet%20that%20it%20will%20help%20get%20something%20weird%20made%20that%20wouldn't%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20doing%20the%20play%20%26quot%3BEquus%26quot%3B%20also%20helped%20me%20from%20a%20critical%20and%20industry%20standpoint.%20I've%20heard%20from%20multiple%20directors%20since%20then%20that%20even%20if%20they%20didn't%20get%20to%20see%20me%20in%20%26quot%3BEquus%2C%26quot%3B%20hearing%20that%20I%20had%20done%20it%20made%20people%20go%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20so%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20this%20more%20than%20just%20a%20minute.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20feel%20%26quot%3BPotter%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20that%20No.%201%2C%20but%20I%20think%20a%20close%20second%20is%20doing%20%26quot%3BEquus.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20condensed%20and%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afd0e0e4-48c2-49fc-a560-46b235c55a8c%5C%22%3EMore%20in%20the%20Role%20Play%20series%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaniel-radcliffe-movies-harry-potter-child-stardom-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772110561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6982562ea645d118818898bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaniel-radcliffe-movies-harry-potter-child-stardom-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20opens%20up%20about%20coping%20with%20fame%20and%20why%20acting%20in%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20best%20business%20decision%20he%20ever%20made.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jguerrasio%40businessinsider.com%20(Jason%20Guerrasio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaniel-radcliffe-movies-harry-potter-child-stardom-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Unhappy%20With%20NCERT%20Judiciary%20Chapter%2C%20Wants%20Accountability%20