re%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESunny%20Stroeer%20left%20Bain%20to%20pursue%20a%20passion%20for%20adventure%20sports%20and%20now%20runs%20outdoor%20businesses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20consulting%20skills%20translated%20well%20into%20managing%20high-stakes%20outdoor%20expeditions%20and%20businesses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20consulting%20experience%20gave%20Stroeer%20confidence%20and%20strategic%20thinking%20for%20entrepreneurial%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20an%20interview%20with%20Sunny%20Stroeer%2C%20a%20professional%20adventure%20athlete%20and%20former%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Econsultant%20at%20Bain%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20who%20left%20in%202015.%20She%20owns%20an%20outdoor%20guiding%20business%20in%20Utah%20and%20has%20an%20expedition%20company%20that%20plans%20trips%20for%20women%20around%20the%20world.%20She's%20also%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Gender%20Equity%20and%20Outdoor%20Adventure.%20Bain%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20relatively%20early%20on%20that%20consulting%20was%20really%20interesting%20and%20rewarding%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20necessarily%20something%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20build%20my%20life%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20six%20months%20before%20my%2030th%20birthday%2C%20I%20had%20a%20pivotal%20experience%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-interview-case-study-ai-test-bcg-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulting%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20my%20longest%20workday%20was%2043%20hours%20straight%20without%20any%20breaks.%20I%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20I%20was%20cutting%20off%20my%20direct%20reports%20after%20four%20words%20if%20they%20weren't%20getting%20to%20the%20point%20fast%20enough%20because%20time%20was%20just%20so%20tight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20like%20the%20person%20that%20I%20was%20becoming%3A%20a%20very%20efficient%2C%20output-oriented%2C%20insecure%2C%20overachiever%2C%20which%20is%20what%20the%20business%20model%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-leaders-consulting-firms-advising-leaders-and-ceos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Three%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20built%20on.%20I%20decided%20that%20even%20though%20it%20was%20professionally%20a%20very%20enriching%20and%20rewarding%20path%2C%20it%20wasn't%20the%20path%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsulting%20was%20an%20eye-opening%20and%20important%20time%20in%20my%20life.%20The%20amount%20that%20I%20learned%20while%20I%20was%20at%20Bain%20was%20bar%20none.%20And%20I%20was%20good%20at%20it.%20I%20didn't%20leave%20because%20I%20couldn't%20hack%20it.%20I%20left%20because%20I%20could%20hack%20it%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20really%20like%20what%20that%20looked%20like%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20person%20that%20made%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20delivered%20that%20case%20successfully%2C%20with%20the%20client%20and%20the%20partner%20thrilled%2C%20and%20then%20walked%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20I%20was%20in%20such%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsultant-left-corporate-stay-at-home-dad-raise-sons-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeep%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20didn't%20see%20another%20way.%20I%20knew%20I%20couldn't%20keep%20going%20the%20way%20I%20was%20going%2C%20and%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20do%20was%20pull%20the%20emergency%20brake%20and%20self-eject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22912d4485-8a30-49ec-83ad-f5a913329983%5C%22%3EI%20became%20an%20adventure%20athlete%20and%20own%20several%20outdoor%20businesses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20knowing%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20some%20time%20to%20explore%20the%20things%20that%20drove%20pure%20joy%20and%20passion%20for%20me%2C%20which%20were%20being%20outside%20and%20having%20adventures.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20concrete%20vision%20for%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20got%20to%20the%20end%20of%20those%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20that%20realm.%20That's%20when%20I%20doubled%20down%20on%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20was%20mostly%20committed%20to%20being%20an%20athlete%20%E2%80%94%20pursuing%20big%20adventures%2C%20big%20climbs%2C%20big%20runs%2C%20accomplishing%20%26quot%3Bfirsts.%26quot%3B%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20career%20around%20it%2C%20actually%2C%20due%20to%20the%20experiences%20that%20I%20had%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffemale-sherpa-climbing-mount-everest-reveals-hardships-in-netflix-documentary-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewoman%20in%20the%20mountains%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Seeing%20gender%20bias%20really%20explicitly%20in%20the%20mountains%20was%20a%20bit%20shocking%20to%20me%20after%20I'd%20spent%20all%20of%20my%2020s%20in%20male-dominated%20environments.%20I%20recognized%20that%20I%20was%20in%20a%20unique%20position%20to%20drive%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20think%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-consultant-quit-hiking-pct-corporate-ladder-career-change-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaving%20consulting%20for%20the%20outdoors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20kind%20of%20sounds%20like%20having%20a%20breakdown%20in%20a%20tent.%20But%20that's%20not%20at%20all%20what%20this%20is%20about.%20Big%20outdoor%20adventure%20is%20as%20high-stakes%2C%20high-pressure%2C%20and%20strategic%20as%20management%20consulting%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20more%20so.%20The%20decisions%20and%20choices%20that%20I%20had%20to%20make%2C%20for%20example%2C%20on%20the%20Iditarod%20Trail%20were%20meaningfully%20more%20strategic%20and%20consequential%20than%20any%20decisions%20I%20ever%20had%20to%20make%20at%20Bain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222977%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunny%20Stroeer%20sitting%20on%20a%20rock%20in%20the%20mountains.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e299850f42603b0f8d6ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222233%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESunny%20Stroeer%20said%20she%20uses%20the%20skills%20she%20developed%20in%20consulting%20both%20as%20an%20athlete%20and%20a%20business%20owner.%3Cp%3ESunny%20Stroeer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-break-into-management-consulting-career-coach-mbb-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuccessful%20consultant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20goal-oriented.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20meticulous%2C%20hardworking%2C%20graceful%20under%20pressure%2C%20an%20excellent%20strategist%2C%20and%20very%20analytical.%20I%20think%20the%20same%20holds%20true%20in%20high-stakes%20outdoor%20adventure.%20There's%20a%20ton%20of%20overlap%20from%20a%20skillset%20and%20personality%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b6934b8-f6b3-4bac-9f4d-658a6a1c2a7c%5C%22%3EConsulting%20prepared%20me%20for%20anything%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20the%20consulting%20toolkit%20and%20pointed%20it%20at%20something%20harder%20and%20that%20I%20was%20passionate%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20out%20and%20pursuing%20adventures%2C%20the%20consequences%20are%20sometimes%20quite%20truly%20life%20or%20death.%20When%20you're%20out%20on%20a%201%2C000-mile%20course%2C%20or%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-honnold-day-in-the-life-routine-professional-rock-climber-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclimbing%20El%20Cap%20in%20Yosemite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20you're%20trying%20to%20set%20a%20speed%20record%2C%20the%20goals%20are%20elective%2C%20but%20the%20choices%20and%20the%20strategic%20options%20are%20very%20high%20stakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20business%20perspective%2C%20what%20I%20did%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20Bain%20is%20one-to-one%20applicable%20to%20what%20I%20do%20now.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20took%20over%20the%20guide%20service%20we%20currently%20run%20in%20Utah%20days%20before%20COVID%20hit.%20I%20was%20essentially%20in%20a%20massive%20crisis%20situation%2C%20facing%20bankruptcy%20and%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20navigate%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20scary%2C%20but%20I%20knew%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20years%20that%20I%20spent%20as%20a%20consultant%2C%20that%20I%20had%20the%20skillset%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20get%20through%20it.%20And%20I%20did.%20We%20grew%20the%20business%20by%20more%20than%20three%20times%20since%202020.%20It%20was%20a%20case%20study%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20business%20owner%2C%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbcg-consultant-burnt-out-left-founded-ai-startup-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulting%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20the%20best%20thing%20that%20could%20have%20happened%20to%20me.%20I%20have%20the%20confidence%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20life%20throws%20my%20way%2C%20I%20know%20how%20to%20think%20about%20coming%20up%20with%20a%20solution.%20You%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20solve%20it%20immediately%2C%20but%20you%20know%20how%20to%20wrap%20your%20arms%20around%20it%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20an%20approachable%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsulting%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20frame%20and%20structure%20things%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20I%20can%20make%20sense%20of%20them%20and%20succeed%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20also%20recognized%20that%20it%20wasn't%20Bain%20that%20put%20me%20into%20burnout.%20What%20put%20me%20into%20burnout%20was%20what%20I%20was%20carrying%20inside%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20the%20desire%20to%20excel%2C%20to%20have%20an%20impact%2C%20and%20to%20do%20things%20as%20well%20as%20I%20possibly%20can%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20still%20carry%20inside%20myself.%20Now%20I%20know%20how%20to%20regulate%20it%20more%20proactively%20and%20thoughtfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunny-stroeer-bain-consultant-quit-burnout-outdoor-adventure-business-athlete-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772109841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e2914e8408f667180324d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunny-stroeer-bain-consultant-quit-burnout-outdoor-adventure-business-athlete-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunny%20Stroeer%20quit%20her%20consulting%20job%20at%20Bain%20and%20built%20a%20career%20on%20outdoor%20adventures.%20She%20said%20she%20uses%20her%20consulting%20skills%20all%20the%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunny-stroeer-bain-consultant-quit-burnout-outdoor-adventure-business-athlete-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sebi%20orders%20regulated%20entities%20to%20disclose%20identity%20on%20social%20media%20posts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772109537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-01%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1769103785-7211.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fsebi-orders-regulated-entities-to-disclose-identity-on-social-media-posts-126022600984_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sebi%20has%20directed%20all%20regulated%20entities%20to%20display%20their%20registered%20name%