20budget%20used%20to%20make%20these%20films.%20From%20the%20mythological%20spectacle%20to%20high-action%20thriller%2C%20films%20like%20%E2%80%98Ramayana%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Toxic%E2%80%99%20are%20surely%20creating%20a%20buzz%2C%20and%20their%20extravagant%20appeal%20is%20strong.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20Bollywood%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20films%20of%202026.Nitesh%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Ramayana%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20developed%20as%20an%20ambitious%2C%20two-part%2C%20live-action%20adaptation%20of%20the%20ancient%20epic.%20While%20the%20buzz%20around%20its%20exact%20budget%20is%20unknown%2C%20as%20per%20reports%2C%20it%20falls%20under%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crores%20to%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore.The%20film%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20VFX-heavy%20spectacle%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20release%20in%20Diwali%202026%20and%202027%20in%20two%20parts.%20The%20first%20part%20is%20expected%20to%20cover%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20early%20life%2C%20his%20wedding%20to%20Sita%2C%20their%20exile%20of%2014%20years%2C%20and%20conclude%20with%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20kidnapping%20by%20Ravan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20justice%20department%20accused%20of%20withholding%20Trump-related%20Epstein%20files%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772108882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F005c%2Flive%2F8f39f990-12e8-11f1-8aab-5db5bc9cf939.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckg3elr1dwpo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20Democrat%20on%20the%20congressional%20panel%20investigating%20Epstein%20has%20called%20on%20the%20attorney%20general%20to%20publish%20the%20material.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckg3elr1dwpo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2