EHe%20spent%20more%20than%20eight%20years%20leading%20the%20organisation%20behind%20the%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-wef-live-updates-jan-19-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econference%20in%20Davos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Switzerland.%20Davos%20is%20one%20of%20the%20set-piece%20events%20on%20the%20business%20calendar%2C%20bringing%20together%20political%20and%20business%20leaders%20to%20discuss%20global%20trends.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigures%20like%20JPMorgan%20CEO%20Jamie%20Dimon%20are%20regular%20attendees%2C%20and%20at%20this%20year's%20event%2C%20speakers%20included%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WEF%20co-chairs%2C%20Andr%C3%A9%20Hoffman%20and%20Larry%20Fink%2C%20said%20the%20independent%20review%20of%20Brende%2C%20which%20was%20made%20public%20earlier%20in%20February%2C%20found%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20no%20additional%20concerns%20beyond%20what%20has%20been%20previously%20disclosed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrende%2C%20a%20former%20Norwegian%20foreign%20minister%2C%20told%20Reuters%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20he%20had%20dinner%20with%20Epstein%20three%20times%20in%202018%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unaware%20of%20Epstein's%20past%20and%20criminal%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrende%20had%2C%20as%20recently%20as%20November%202025%2C%20denied%20knowing%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%20was%20first%20convicted%20in%202008%20of%20procuring%20a%20minor%20for%20prostitution.%20He%20was%20charged%20with%20the%20sex%20trafficking%20of%20minors%20in%20July%202019%20and%20died%20in%20jail%20the%20following%20month%20while%20awaiting%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20arranged%20a%20dinner%20at%20Epstein's%20New%20York%20home%20in%20September%202018%2C%20on%20Brende's%2053rd%20birthday%2C%20according%20to%20emails%20released%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20email%20exchanges%