%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Citro%20Alexander%20was%20about%2011%20years%20old%20when%20she%20first%20realized%20her%20health%20was%20linked%20to%20every%20bite%20of%20food%20she%20ate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20an%20Italian-American%20family%2C%20food%20was%20part%20of%20her%20culture.%20Meals%20were%20home-cooked%2C%20nutritious%20but%20quite%20rich%3A%20heaping%20helpings%20of%20Grandma's%20lasagna%2C%20with%20a%20side%20of%20spinach%20and%20fruit%20for%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20around%20the%20time%20her%20age%20hit%20double%20digits%2C%20she%20started%20to%20suffer%20from%20severe%20bloating%20and%20unpleasant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-symptoms-unhealthy-gut-how-to-fix-gastrenterologist-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigestive%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20hours%20after%20every%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20stomach%20would%20feel%20like%20a%20bowling%20ball%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20still%20feel%20it%20viscerally%20to%20this%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20medical%20appointments%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Ffodmap-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelimination%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20learned%20that%20dairy%20was%20one%20culprit%20in%20her%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20first%20moment%20that%20I%20remember%20realizing%20that%20food%20could%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20my%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20two%20decades%20later%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20is%20CEO%20of%20FoodHealth%20Company%2C%20which%20uses%20a%20food%20scoring%20system%20to%20help%20consumers%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20It's%20a%20resource%20she%20said%20she%20could%20have%20used%20years%20ago%20as%20she%20struggled%20to%20manage%20digestive%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20eating%20a%20bit%20from%20a%20noodle%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f409ae8408f667180407b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESharing%20her%20own%20experience%20is%20part%20of%20Citro%20Alexander's%20passion%20for%20making%20healthy%20eating%20more%20accessible.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sam%20Citro%20Alexander%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20her%2030s%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20said%20she's%20dialed%20in%20her%20nutrition%20for%20more%20energy%2C%20healthier%20skin%20and%20hair%2C%20and%20better%20digestion%20by%20focusing%20on%20simple%2C%20everyday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-improve-gut-health-with-food-full-meals-dietitian-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efoods%20for%20gut%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a7c994f-0150-46a7-8f9f-fc64d8a7c89b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReducing%20inflammation%2C%20healing%20the%20gut%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECitro%20Alexander%20spent%20her%20late%20teens%20and%2020s%20battling%20digestive%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20she%20relied%20on%20cheap%20convenience%20food%20and%20takeout.%20The%20%26quot%3Bprocessed%20crap%26quot%3B%20didn't%20make%20her%20feel%20great%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20body%20of%20research%20suggests%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ultra-processed-foods-impact-your-body-calories-weight-gain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprocessed%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20cause%20of%20multitude%20of%20health%20harms%2C%20from%20increasing%20risk%20of%20cancer%20and%20heart%20disease%20to%20speeding%20cognitive%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResolved%20to%20cook%20more%20at%20home%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20started%20going%20to%20the%20farmers%20market%20to%20load%20up%20on%20new-to-her%20ingredients%20like%20dried%20beans%20and%20Swiss%20Chard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20found%20an%20unlikely%20inspiration%20at%20work.%20Through%20her%20former%20marketing%20and%20development%20role%20skincare%20industry%2C%20she%20routinely%20used%20plant-based%20ingredients%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fturmeric-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturmeric%20to%20reduce%20inflammation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20trip%20to%20Indonesia%2C%20she%20discovered%20how%20many%20herbs%20and%20spices%20could%20have%20digestive%20benefits%2C%20too%2C%20prepared%20in%20flavorful%20meals%20or%20warming%20teas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20taking%20a%20cooking%20class%20outdoors%20in%20Indonesia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f40241fb3fcb426487140%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECitro%20Alexander%20said%20a%20medicinal%20cooking%20class%20she%20took%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Indonesia%20opened%20her%20eyes%20to%20the%20healing%20power%20of%20food.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sam%20Citro%20Alexander%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20revelation%20to%20reframe%20healthy%20eating%20as%20adding%20more%20nutritious%20foods%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20what%20to%20cut%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20avoiding%20badness%20doesn't%20really%20give%20your%20body%20what%20it%20needs.%20You%20need%20to%20fuel%20it%20with%20goodness%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22228cc363-8d8e-4e31-851d-82969a90da0e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20typical%20day%20of%20eating%20for%20better%20gut%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20said%20her%20daily%20routine%20includes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquick-easy-high-protein-high-fiber-breakfast-every-morning-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-fiber%2C%20high-protein%20breakfast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20tea%2C%20bone%20broth%2C%20farmers%20market%20veggies%2C%20and%20fresh%20herbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20starts%20the%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-your-own-electrolyte-drink-for-better-hydration-dietitian-recipe-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehomemade%20electrolyte%20drink%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20a%20tall%20glass%20of%20water%20with%20lemon%2C%20cayenne%2C%20and%20sea%20salt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20breakfast%2C%20her%20go-to%20choice%20is%20a%20protein%20smoothie%20alongside%20whole-grain%20toast%20with%20avocado%20(which%20offers%20healthy%20fats%20in%20addition%20to%20fiber).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20day%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20said%20she%20drinks%20several%20teas%20and%20herbal%20infusions.%20These%20infusions%20can%20be%20rich%20in%20polyphenols%20and%20other%20plant-based%20micronutrients%2C%20and%20are%20as%20simple%20to%20make%20as%20steeping%20fresh%20ginger%20in%20hot%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223723%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20a%20cup%20of%20herbal%20tea%20being%20poured%20from%20a%20teapot%20on%20a%20tray%20of%20dried%20citrus%20and%20spices%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cc2712237a6a8f0cdb0c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrinking%20tea%20is%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20incorporate%20more%20plant-based%20nutrients%20into%20your%20routine.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Falls%20Commercial%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20lunch%2C%20she%20often%20turns%20to%20salad%20or%20a%20grain%20bowl%20packed%20with%20more%20veggies%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20herbs%2C%20beans%2C%20farro%20or%20quinoa%2C%20according%20to%20recipes%20she's%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20dinnertime%2C%20Citro%20Alexander%20has%20a%20rotating%20menu%20of%20recipes.%20A%20favorite%20is%20soba%20noodles%20with%20bone%20broth%2C%20which%20is%20high%20in%20collagen%20protein%20for%20healthy%20joints%2C%20skin%2C%20and%20hair.%20She%20adds%20plenty%20of%20ginger%2C%20lemongrass%2C%20and%20chiles%20for%20a%20punch%20of%20flavor%20and%20even%20more%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20her%20Italian%20roots%2C%20she%20also%20makes%20plenty%20of%20classic%20pasta%20dishes%20with%20sauce%20using%20extra-virgin%20olive%20oil%2C%20herbs%2C%20and%20veggies%20from%20the%20garden%20or%20farmers%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocally-grown%20produce%20can%20be%20more%20nutritious%20than%20what%20you'd%20buy%20at%20a%20big-box%20grocery%20store%2C%20since%20commercial%20fruits%20and%20veggies%20are%20often%20less%20fresh%20and%20grown%20for%20durability%2C%20not%20flavor%20or%20vitamin%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b723938b-a733-4878-8895-f1dff6375b6a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20start%20eating%20healthy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECitro%20Alexander%20said%20her%20best%20advice%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20eat%20healthier%20is%20to%20start%20cooking%20simple%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPick%20one%20meal%20a%20day%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20make%20from%20whole%20foods%2C%20whichever%20ones%20you%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20cooking%20for%20yourself%2C%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20control%20over%20what%20you%20put%20into%20your%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitro%20Alexander%20turned%20her%20own%20struggles%20into%20the%20FoodHealth%20score%20to%20help%20highlight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-ultra-processed-food-healthier-add-vegetables-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebetter-for-you%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intention%20is%20to%20help%20people%20prevent%20and%20manage%20chronic%20disease%2C%26quot%3B%20Citro%20Alexander%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20best%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20to%20eat%20a%20diet%20that%20is%20rich%20in%20fruit%2C%20vegetables%2C%2