's%20in%20a%20head-to-head%20trial.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPatients%20on%20Lilly's%20pill%20had%20better%20blood%20sugar%20levels%2C%20lost%20more%20weight%2C%20and%20improved%20heart%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pill%2C%20which%20analysts%20say%20might%20cost%20%24300%20a%20month%2C%20could%20be%20available%20as%20soon%20as%20mid-2026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBetter%20injections%20and%20better%20pills.%20It's%20official%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Feli-lilly%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEli%20Lilly%3C%2Fa%3E%20appears%20to%20be%20beating%20Novo%20Nordisk%20at%20the%20weight%20loss%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Lilly%20announced%20that%20its%20forthcoming%20GLP-1%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-new-weight-loss-pill-orforglipron-retatrutide-trial-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epill%2C%20called%20orforglipron%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bested%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20existing%20oral%20semaglutide%20pill%20in%20a%20large%20head-to-head%20clinical%20trial.%20(Lilly's%20injectable%20GLP-1%20drug%20tirzepatide%20already%20beat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ozempic-wegovy-actually-work-telling-brain-to-feel-full-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einjectable%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20another%20head-to-head%20trial%20last%20year.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELilly's%20pill%20%26quot%3Boutperformed%26quot%3B%20Novo's%20%26quot%3Bon%20every%20key%20endpoint%20we%20measured%2C%20including%20A1C%20and%20weight%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20lead%20trial%20investigator%20Dr.%20Julio%20Rosenstock%2C%20an%20endocrinologist%20and%20diabetes%20and%20metabolism%20expert%2C%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%2C%20which%20lasted%20for%20one%20year%20and%20included%201%2C698%20patients%20with%20diabetes%20on%20three%20continents%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20big%20win%20for%20Lilly%2C%20which%20has%20been%20racing%20ahead%20of%20its%20competitors%20in%20developing%20new%20and%20improved%20formulations%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20the%20breakout%20star%20with%20Ozempic%2C%20Novo%20Nordisk%20has%20struggled%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20new%20winner%2C%20with%20its%20latest%20results%20on%20the%20new%20investigational%20drug%20CagriSema%20underwhelming%20investors%20earlier%20this%20week.%20If%20all%20goes%20well%20with%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20orforglipron%20could%20be%20available%20to%20US%20consumers%20by%20this%20spring%2C%20with%20prices%20rivaling%20a%20%26quot%3Bfancy%20gym%20membership%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20one%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cf58914-f919-4b32-abd1-5a9d0a3cae12%5C%22%3E15%20to%2020%20pounds%20of%20weight%20loss%20and%20heart%20health%20benefits%2C%20but%20more%20side%20effects%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22heart%20rate%20monitor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f5a2fe8408f66718043c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20drug%20improved%20blood%20sugar%20control%2C%20but%20also%20prompted%20weight%20loss%20and%20heart%20health%20benefits.%3Cp%3EDavizro%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20Nordisk's%20existing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-pills-coming-but-may-not-be-convenient-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20pill%2C%20Rybelsus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20FDA%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20diabetes%20in%202019.%20It's%20a%20once-daily%20formulation%20that%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach%20with%20only%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELilly's%20new%20orforglipron%20would%20have%20none%20of%20those%20restrictions.%20It%20can%20be%20taken%20at%20any%20time%20of%20day%2C%20with%20or%20without%20food.%20It's%20also%20looking%20more%20powerful%20than%20Rybelsus%2C%20in%20part%20because%20the%20dosages%20tested%20were%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20trial%2C%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736(26)00202-3%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20patients%20on%207%20to%2014%20milligrams%20of%20Rybelsus%20lost%2C%20on%20average%2C%20between%208%20and%2011%20pounds%2C%20while%20patients%20on%2012%20to%2036%20milligrams%20of%20orforglipron%20lost%20an%20average%20of%2015%20to%2020%20pounds%2C%20roughly%20the%20same%20level%20of%20weight%20loss%20that%20people%20with%20diabetes%20tend%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eachieve%20when%20taking%20Ozempic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20blood%20sugar%20control%20and%20weight%20loss%20benefits%2C%20orforglipron%20takers%20had%20more%20meaningful%20improvements%20to%20their%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20blood%20pressure%20readings%2C%20and%20triglycerides%20than%20Rybelsus%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20the%20field%20is%20moving%20toward%20treatments%20that%20meaningfully%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-mounjaro-zepbound-approved-weight-loss-stronger-than-wegovy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimprove%20weight%2C%20blood%20sugar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20risk%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Naveed%20Sattar%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20cardiometabolic%20medicine%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Glasgow%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20this%20study%2C%20said%20in%20a%20release.%20%26quot%3BThese%20more%20holistic%20approaches%2C%20which%20also%20benefit%20patient%20well-being%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20offer%20the%20greatest%20benefits%20for%20people%20living%20with%20type%202%20diabetes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%3F%20A%20stronger%20drug%20regimen%20means%20more%20side%20effects.%20Roughly%2010%25%20of%20patients%20on%20the%20highest%20dose%20of%20orforglipron%20quit%20this%20trial%20early%2C%20complaining%20of%20gastrointestinal%20issues%20including%20nausea%2C%20diarrhea%2C%20and%20indigestion.%20Only%20about%205%25%20of%20people%20on%20the%20highest%20dose%20of%20Rybelsus%20quit%20because%20of%20side%20effects%20like%20that.%20Business%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20Rybelsus%20maker%20Novo%20Nordisk%20for%20comment%20on%20this%20study%2C%20but%20did%20not%20immediately%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22881ee7ac-b77f-4561-b6d9-d3a1679226b0%5C%22%3EOrforglipron%20could%20hit%20shelves%20in%202026%2C%20and%20Eli%20Lilly%20has%20already%20ramped%20up%20its%20production%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223587%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eli%20lilly%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f4d6be8408f66718041ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222392%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEli%20Lilly%20has%20been%20building%20out%20its%20manufacturing%20capacity%2C%20racing%20to%20meet%20demand%20for%20GLP-1s.%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-new-weight-loss-pill-orforglipron-retatrutide-trial-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEli%20Lilly%20Executive%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vice%20President%20Ken%20Custer%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20is%20already%20manufacturing%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20orforglipron%20pills%20at%20a%20facility%20in%20Huntsville%2C%20Alabama%2C%20just%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20can%20meet%20demand%20ASAP%20if%20and%20when%20the%20drug%20is%20approved%20for%20use%20in%20the%20US.%20Lilly%20is%20betting%20that%20approval%20could%20come%20before%20the%20summertime%2C%20with%20an%20initial%20approval%20for%20obesity%20possible%20as%20early%20as%20April%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20daily%20pill%20requires%20more%20obedience%20than%20a%20weekly%20shot%2C%20it%20has%20a%20few%20advantages.%20First%2C%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20much%20cheaper.%20Deutsche%20Bank's%20director%20of%20biopharma%20equity%20research%2C%20James%20Shin%2C%20said%20it%20would%20be%20comparable%20to%20buying%20a%20%26quot%3Bfancy%20gym%20membership.%26quot%3B%20He%20estimated%20the%20list%20price%20for%20orforglipron%20could%20start%20at%20around%20%24300%20(far%20cheaper%20than%20the%20%241%2C000%2B%20price%20tags%20on%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20Mounjaro%2C%20and%20Tirzepatide).%20Clinical%20trials%20have%20also%20shown%20that%20orforglipron%20can%20help%20patients%20who've%20already%20been%20on%20an%20injectable%20GLP-1%20maintain%20their%20weight%20loss%20if%20they%20choose%20to%20stop%20taking%20the%20drug%2C%20acting%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-weight-gain-after-ozempic-with-maintenance-dose-doctor-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaintenance%20medication%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20since%20this%20is%20a%20small%20molecule%2C%20it%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20refrigerated%2C%20a%20huge%20win%20for%20global%20distribution%20and%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20more%20than%20one%20billion%20people%20across%20the%20globe%20that%20are%20suffering%20from%20obesity%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrik%20Jonsson%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Lilly%20International%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20way%20that%20we%20can%20meet%20those%20demands%20with%20injectable%20treatments%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%