%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ff5ab1fb3fcb426487b99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222820%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECindy%20Rose%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20WPP.%20%3Cp%3EWPP%2FJillian%20Edelstein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWPP's%20new%20CEO%2C%20Cindy%20Rose%2C%20has%20set%20out%20her%20turnaround%20plan%20for%20the%20ailing%20ad%20giant.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20simplifying%20WPP's%20structure%20and%20targeting%20about%20%24676%20million%20in%20cost%20savings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20her%20transformation%20strategy%20means%20for%20WPP's%2098%2C000%20staffers%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20is%20entering%20a%20new%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20ad%20giant's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-cindy-rose-first-100-days-as-wpp-ceo-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%2C%20Cindy%20Rose%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20unveiled%20a%20sweeping%20turnaround%20plan%20as%20the%20company%20grapples%20with%20cost-cutting%20clients%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ipg-deal-signals-major-shift-ad-agency-market-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintensifying%20competition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-changing-advertising-agency-business-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20disruption%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20is%20taking%20a%20sledgehammer%20to%20WPP's%20operating%20model%20and%20streamlining%20the%20company%20into%20four%20key%20units.%20The%20ad%20giant%20previously%20operated%20as%20a%20holding%20company%2C%20where%20an%20alphabet%20soup%20of%20different%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20from%20creative%20to%20PR%20and%20production%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20worked%20in%20silos.%20WPP%20is%20also%20doubling%20down%20on%20AI%20and%20forming%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Benterprise%20solutions%26quot%3B%20division%20to%20help%20clients%20with%20their%20own%20AI%20transformations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20anticipates%20achieving%20cost%20savings%20of%20%C2%A3500%20million%2C%20about%20%24676%20million%2C%20by%202028%20as%20part%20of%20the%20strategy.%20The%20market%20did%20not%20react%20favorably%20to%20the%20plan.%20WPP%20shares%20slid%20more%20than%206%25%20in%20early%20London%20trading%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwpp-ceo-cindy-rose-microsoft-lawyer-ad-agency-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etook%20the%20helm%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20ad%20giant%20in%20September%2C%20and%20WPP's%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20Joanne%20Wilson%2C%20held%20a%20call%20with%20reporters%20on%20Thursday%20morning%20about%20their%20%26quot%3BElevate28%26quot%3B%20strategy.%20Here%20are%20the%20key%20takeaways%2C%20and%20what%20the%20reset%20means%20for%20WPP's%2098%2C000%20staffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b6df5c2-0091-4b46-9f84-d9e320504a4c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20The%20brutal%20financials%20require%20cost-cutting%2C%20which%20could%20mean%20layoffs%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20acknowledged%20on%20the%20call%20that%20the%20financials%20aren't%20pretty.%20%26quot%3BOur%20performance%20is%20not%20where%20it%20needs%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20full-year%20revenue%20for%202025%20fell%2010.4%25%20to%20%C2%A310.1%20billion%2C%20around%20%2413.7%20billion%2C%20while%20its%20operating%20profit%20slumped%20more%20than%2070%25%20to%20%C2%A3382%20million%2C%20around%20%24517%20million.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20was%20hit%20by%20clients%20cutting%20back%20spending%20in%20sectors%20including%20tech%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20consumer%20goods.%20It%20was%20also%20impacted%20by%20large%20goodwill%20and%20property-related%20impairment%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20warned%20the%20bleeding%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20until%20at%20least%20the%20back%20half%20of%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20did%20not%20provide%20specifics%20when%20asked%20how%20cuts%20might%20translate%20into%20layoffs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20company%20has%20identified%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20initiatives%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20its%20%24676%20million%20cost-saving%20goal%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Beliminating%20some%20duplication%20in%20certain%20areas%2C%20org%20simplification%2C%20shared%20services%20in%20the%20finance%20and%20HR%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20alongside%20managing%20its%20real%20estate%20portfolio.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20emphasized%20that%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20these%20cost%20savings%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20reinvested%20into%20high-growth%20areas%20of%20the%20business%2C%20including%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c3a3f03-6fc0-4fea-a158-587b97a9e69c%5C%22%3E2.%20Unification%20is%20the%20hottest%20trend%20in%20advertising%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20former%20CEO%2C%20Martin%20Sorrell%2C%20WPP%20pioneered%20the%20advertising%20agency%20holding%20company%20model.%20That%20blueprint%20is%20unraveling%20across%20Madison%20Avenue%2C%20reflecting%20clients'%20desire%20for%20a%20simpler%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP's%20French%20rival%2C%20Publicis%2C%20unveiled%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaurice-levy-will-still-be-part-of-publicis-despite-retirement-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epower%20of%20one%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20structure%20a%20decade%20ago.%20The%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ceo-john-wren-ipg-merger-ai-job-cuts-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOmnicom-IPG%20mega-merger%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20together%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20creative%2C%20PR%2C%20health%2C%20media%2C%20and%20production%20agencies%20under%20one%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20it's%20WPP's%20turn.%20It's%20simplifying%20its%20business%20into%20four%20divisions%3A%20WPP%20Media%2C%20WPP%20Creative%2C%20WPP%20Production%2C%20and%20WPP%20Enterprise%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rationalization%20likely%20won't%20be%20without%20pain.%20A%20former%20Publicis%20exec%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20some%20leaders%20were%20roiled%20when%20the%20French%20ad%20group%20went%20through%20a%20similar%20process.%20Some%20felt%20their%20power%20and%20responsibilities%20were%20diminished%2C%20and%20that%20their%20performance%20was%20less%20visible%20to%20senior%20leadership%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20did%20get%20them%20to%20a%20better%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgroupm-simplify-business-country-level-strategy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eformer%20Publicis%20exec%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%202023%20interview.%20%26quot%3BBut%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20ended%20up%20leaving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20acknowledged%20on%20Thursday's%20call%20that%20times%20of%20change%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Banxiety-inducing%26quot%3B%20for%20staffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20transformation%20fatigue%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20plan%20is%20designed%20to%20get%20us%20to%20end%20of%20job%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%20within%20the%20next%2018%20months.%20So%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20draw%20this%20out%20for%20any%20longer%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286f58cf1-d13d-402c-863b-27b3c026679e%5C%22%3E3.%20Tired%3A%20Advertising.%20Wired%3A%20Consulting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20of%20creating%20and%20placing%20ads%20has%20become%20commoditized%20and%20less%20lucrative%20over%20the%20years%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shift%20now%20accelerating%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20where%20logos%20and%20campaigns%20can%20be%20generated%20in%20seconds%20and%20deployed%20through%20automated%20platforms.%20Agencies%20have%20responded%20by%20pushing%20beyond%20their%20creative%20roots%2C%20expanding%20into%20areas%20like%20data%2C%20commerce%2C%20and%20digital%20transformation%20as%20they%20try%20to%20reinvent%20themselves%20as%20strategic%20advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20thinking%20behind%20WPP's%20new%20enterprise%20solutions%20unit.%20It's%20a%20play%20to%20lock%20in%20longer-term%2C%20management-consulting-style%20contracts%2C%20combining%20its%20capabilities%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20customer%20experience%20and%20technology%20integration.%20Right%20now%2C%20nearly%20every%20global%20business%20is%20trying%20to%20identify%20its%20AI%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20WPP%20wants%20to%20be%20on%20hand%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20mission%20is%20now%20to%20be%20a%20trusted%20growth%20partner%20for%20our%20clients%20in%20the%20era%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said%20on%20Thursday's%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELove%20it%20or%20loathe%20it%2C%20WPP%20staffers%20are%20expected%20to%20embrace%20AI%2C%20too.%20Rose%20said%20the%20company%20is%20bringing%20WPP%20Open%2C%20its%20agentic%20marketing%20platform%2C%20%26quot%3Bin%20every%20single%20client%20pitch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20head-to-head%20with%20consulting%20giants%20won't%20be%20easy.%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20analyst%20Matthew%20Bloxham%20wrote%20in%20a%20Thursday%20research%20note%20that%20while%20WPP's%20generative-AI%20offerings%20%26quot%3Blook%20impressive%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20only%20mirror%20similar%20industry-wide%20initiatives.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWPP's%20new%20Elevate28%20strategy%20doesn't%20go%20far%20enough%20to%20deliver%20the%20course%20correction%20required%20to%20address%20concerns%20about%20the%20existential%20threat%20from%20AI%20to%20the%20global%20advertising%20agency's%20business%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloxham%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwpp-turnaround-plan-3-key-takeaways-staff-cost-cutting-advertising-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772103944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ff5ab1fb3fcb426487b99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwpp-turnaround-plan-3-key-takeaways-staff-cost-cutting-advertising-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20big%20changes%20ahead%20at%20WPP.%20The%20British%20ad%20group%20is%20simplifying%20its%20structure%20and%20planning%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20cost%20savings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwpp-turnaround-plan-3-key-takeaways-staff-cost-cutting-advertising-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Red%20Lobster's%20wunderkind%20CEO%20might%20have%20the%20secret%20sauce%20for%20turnarounds.%20Private%20equity%20should%20be%20taking%20notes.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iconic%20Red%20Lobster%20sign%20is%20seen%20from%20the%20highway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e50651fb3fcb426486499%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223799%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Red%20Lobster%20sign%20in%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Kosienski%2FSipa%20USA%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20Business%20Insider%20Today%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Ivy%20League-educated%2C%20former%20private-equity%20investor%20with%20a%20knack%20for%20chasing%20turnarounds%20doesn't%20sound%20like%20a%20sympathetic%20figure.%20Damola%20Adamolekun%20is%20different.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20Red%20Lobster%20CEO%20is%20the%20face%20of%20the%20seafood%20chain's%20turnaround%2C%20building%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-bankruptcy-rebound-endless-shrimp-private-equity-adamolekun-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecult%20following%20along%20the%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20writes%20BI's%20Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20traditional%20Wall%20Street%20tactics%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-endless-shrimp-bankruptcy-private-equity-debt-real-estate-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esale-leasebacks%20on%20the%20restaurants'%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20what%20got%20Red%20Lobster%20in%20trouble%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20(The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-home-of-the-endless-shrimp-mulls-bankruptcy-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendless%20shrimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20help.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Adamolekun%20has%20taken%20a%20different%20approach%20from%20the%20slash-and-burn%20strategy%20PE%20is%20commonly%20criticized%20for%2C%20making%20him%20a%20fan%20favorite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20in%20familiar%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20Paulson%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20he%20pitched%20an%20investment%20in%20struggling%20chain%20P.F.%20Chang's.%20By%202020%2C%20he%20was%20named%20CEO.%20He%20eventually%20helped%20it%20bring%20in%20an%20additional%20%241%20billion%20in%20revenue%20before%20stepping%20down%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20at%20Red%20Lobster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-rise-and-fall-bankruptcy-history-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20even%20more%20dire%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20joined%20in%202024%2C%20as%20the%20chain%20was%20emerging%20from%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy.%20Since%20then%2C%20Adamolekun%20has%20done%20everything%20from%20giving%20the%20menu%20a%20facelift%20to%20creating%20value-focused%20meals%20that%20won't%20break%20the%20bottom%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-bankruptcy-rebound-endless-shrimp-private-equity-adamolekun-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Katherine%20writes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20CEO%20with%20a%20wide-ranging%20fan%20base%2C%20from%20former%20Red%20Lobster%20fans%20who%20drifted%20from%20the%20brand%20to%20finance%20bros%20impressed%20with%20his%20handiwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Damola%20Adamolekun%20standing%20in%20suit%20with%20hands%20folded%20in%20front%20of%20a%20restaurant%20bench.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a62ce7eb4be2fff9a3ec14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226192%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDamola%20Adamolekun%20standing%20in%20suit%20with%20hands%20folded%20in%20front%20of%20a%20restaurant%20bench.%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Bruzzese%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20only%20fair%20I%20disclose%20my%20personal%20bias%3A%20I%20grew%20up%20%3Cem%3Eloving%3C%2Fem%3E%20Red%20Lobster.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20frequented%20our%20fair%20share%20of%20casual%20dining%20chains%20growing%20up%2C%20but%20a%20seafood-hating%20mother%20and%20sister%20meant%20Red%20Lobster%20was%20rarely%20in%20the%20rotation.%20On%20the%20one%20day%20a%20year%20I'd%20get%20to%20pick%20(my%20birthday)%2C%20it%20was%20%3Cem%3Ealways%3C%2Fem%3E%20going%20to%20be%20Red%20Lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(The%20high%20from%20ordering%20an%20Ultimate%20Feast%20as%20a%2010-year-old%20is%20honestly%20a%20feeling%20I'm%20still%20chasing%20to%20this%20day.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20some%20point%2C%20things%20changed.%20Those%20corporate%20chains%20started%20feeling%20a%20lot%20more%20soul%20sucking.%20I%20couldn't%20look%20at%20a%20server%20without%20thinking%20of%20Jennifer%20Aniston's%20character%20in%20%26quot%3BOffice%20Space%26quot%3B%20getting%20yelled%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF7SNEdjftno%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20not%20having%20enough%20flair%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamolekun's%20willingness%20to%20put%20himself%20in%20front%20of%20the%20turnaround%20has%20helped%20change%20that%20vibe.%20That%2C%20coupled%20with%20his%20patience%20in%20implementing%20changes%2C%20is%20a%20lesson%20for%20other%20aspiring%20PE-turned-CEOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20trillions%20in%20PE%20capital%20sitting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20and%20big%20questions%20about%20AI's%20impact%20on%20legacy%20businesses%2C%20there%20will%20probably%20be%20no%20shortage%20of%20turnaround%20opportunities%20for%20PE.%20Adamolekun's%20playbook%20could%20be%20one%20worth%20replicating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20have%20my%20next%20birthday%20meal%20picked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-damola-adamolekun-turnaround-new-menu-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772103932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f7ba2e8408f6671804850%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-damola-adamolekun-turnaround-new-menu-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Red%20Lobster's%20wunderkind%20CEO%20might%20have%20the%20secret%20sauce%20for%20turnarounds.%20Private%20equity%20should%20be%20taking%20notes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-damola-adamolekun-turnaround-new-menu-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic%20has%20less%20than%2036%20hours%20before%20it%20barrels%20toward%20uncharted%20territory%20with%20the%20US%20government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dario%20Amodei%3B%20Pete%20Hegseth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e3aef50f42603b0f8d78f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic's%20military%20contract%20has%20come%20under%20threat%20following%20a%20meeting%20between%20the%20AI%20company's%20CEO%20and%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth.%3Cp%3EChance%20Yeh%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20HubSpot%3B%20AAron%20Ontiveroz%2FThe%20Denver%20Post%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20and%20the%20US%20government%20are%20at%20a%20standstill%20over%20the%20use%20of%20the%20company's%20Claude%20model.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Pentagon%20is%20pressing%20Anthropic%20to%20accept%20its%20terms%20or%20lose%20its%20military%20contract.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESources%20said%20the%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20use%202%20levers%20to%20compel%20Anthropic%20to%20agree.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20is%20fast-approaching%20uncharted%20waters%20with%20the%20US%20government%20over%20military%20use%20of%20its%20frontier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-ai-tools-tech-selloff-software-apocalypse-cybersecurity-anthropic-ibm-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20model%2C%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%3C%2Fa%3E%20talked%20with%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20in%20a%20meeting%20that%20a%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider%20was%20friendly%20and%20respectful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%2C%20however%2C%20ended%20with%20a%20warning%20to%20Anthropic%3A%20Get%20on%20board%20with%20the%20military%20or%20risk%20getting%20what%20amounts%20to%20a%20blacklisting%20by%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Pentagon%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Anthropic%20has%20until%205%3A01%20p.m.%20Eastern%20Time%20on%20Friday%20to%20agree%20to%20the%20Defense%20Department's%20terms%3B%20otherwise%2C%20it%20will%20find%20other%20levers%20to%20compel%20the%20AI%20startup%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20Hegseth%20is%20prepared%20for%20the%20use%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-defense-production-act-why-it-matters-coronavirus-explained-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDefense%20Production%20Act%20(DPA)%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decades-old%20wartime%20law%20that%20gives%20the%20president%20broad%20authority%20over%20private%20companies%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20national%20security%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20designating%20Anthropic%20a%20supply%20chain%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20terms%20the%20military%20is%20demanding%20of%20Anthropic%20are%20unclear%2C%20but%20the%20warnings%20against%20a%20US%20company%20over%20broad%20access%20to%20a%20frontier%20model%20represent%20novel%20uses%20of%20national%20emergency%20authorities%20against%20a%20novel%20technology%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20absolutely%20in%20uncharted%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Dean%20Ball%2C%20an%20ex-senior%20policy%20advisor%20for%20the%20White%20House%20Office%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Policy%20and%20fellow%20for%20the%20Foundation%20for%20American%20Innovation%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5ca9a1c-dbed-487b-88fd-bec55ea0cd42%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20cordial%20meeting%20with%20an%20ultimatum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20July%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20an%20AI%20startup%20backed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-bet-anthropic-soars-61-billion-valuation-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20and%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20awarded%20a%20contract%20with%20a%20%24200%20million%20ceiling%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20to%20develop%20%26quot%3Bfrontier%20AI%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Baddress%20critical%20national%20security%20challenges%20in%20across%20warfighting%20and%20enterprise%20domains%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20was%20the%20only%20AI%20company%20at%20the%20time%20to%20be%20cleared%20to%20operate%20models%20in%20classified%20settings.%20Grok%2C%20which%20is%20developed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20received%20a%20similar%20approval%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20and%20others%20are%20close%20to%20getting%20on%20board%2C%20a%20senior%20Pentagon%20official%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20months%20after%20Anthropic%20received%20the%20contract%2C%20the%20defense%20secretary%20delivered%20a%20speech%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk's%20SpaceX%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hegseth%20framed%20AI%20innovation%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwartime%20arms%20race%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20the%20accelerated%20deployment%20of%20frontier%20models%20for%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speech%20even%20took%20an%20ideological%20bent.%20The%20defense%20secretary%20railed%20against%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-wrongly-flagged-jobs-programs-dei-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDEI%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bdays%20of%20equitable%20AI%26quot%3B%20are%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20employ%20AI%20models%20that%20won't%20allow%20you%20to%20fight%20wars%2C%26quot%3B%20Hegseth%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Amodei%20met%20with%20the%20defense%20secretary%20at%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20during%20which%20the%20CEO%20showed%20%26quot%3Bappreciation%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20DOD's%20service%20and%20%26quot%3Bthanked%26quot%3B%20Hegseth%2C%20an%20Anthropic%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20subject%20they%20broached%20was%20around%20Anthropic's%20red%20lines%3A%20autonomous%20weapons%20and%20mass%20surveillance%20of%20domestic%20citizens%2C%20according%20to%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esource%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Pentagon%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20standstill%20with%20Anthropic%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20startup's%20redlines.%20There's%20also%20no%20public%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20the%20DOD%20had%20some%20ideological%20or%20political%20issue%20with%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20cordial%20meeting%2C%20Amodei%20was%20left%20with%20an%20ultimatum%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20Ball%20said%20could%20send%20%26quot%3Bawful%20signals%26quot%3B%20to%20US%20entrepreneurs%20and%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bexistential%26quot%3B%20for%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20startup%2C%20this%20week%2C%20released%20an%20update%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-changing-safety-policy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternal%20safety%20framework%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20draws%20a%20clearer%20line%20between%20the%20safeguards%20it%20commits%20to%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bmore%20ambitious%20industry-wide%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20stating%20that%20it%20supports%20the%20latter%20but%20can't%20follow%20them%20%26quot%3Bunilaterally%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Anthropic%20said%20the%20framework%20update%20was%20unrelated%20to%20the%20situation%20with%20the%20Defense%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec8c6ab5-d09f-41c9-b7c2-7a8c1a358c8b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnthropic's%20'existential'%20threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBall%2C%20who%20helped%20draft%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20%26quot%3BAI%20Action%20Plan%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20Defense%20Department%20is%20using%20the%20DPA%20and%20the%20supply%20chain%20risk%20label%20in%20fairly%20unprecedented%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DPA%20was%20established%20during%20the%20Korean%20War%20to%20give%20the%20executive%20branch%20broad%20authority%20over%20how%20to%20invest%20and%20spend%20resources%2C%20particularly%20to%20ramp%20up%20physical%20production%20in%20factories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20was%20used%20on%20American%20companies%20many%20times%2C%20Ball%20said%2C%20but%20more%20frequently%20to%20invest%20in%20firms%20to%20help%20expand%20production.%20The%20Defense%20Department%20is%20instead%20proposing%20to%20use%20Title%20I%20of%20the%20act%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20government%20to%20tell%20companies%20how%20to%20deploy%20their%20economic%20resources%2C%20in%20order%20to%20compel%20a%20company%20to%20agree%20to%20its%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20aware%20of%20this%20ever%20having%20been%20used%20as%20a%20weapon%20in%20a%20negotiating%20posture%2C%26quot%3B%20Ball%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeirdre%20Mulligan%2C%20faculty%20director%20of%20the%20Berkeley%20Center%20for%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20DPA%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20used%20as%20a%20last-resort%20tool%20when%20no%20other%20alternatives%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20pretty%20extraordinary%20use%20or%20potential%20use%20of%20the%20DPA%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20supply%20chain%20risk%20designation%20is%20also%20novel%20since%20it's%20often%20applied%20to%20foreign%20or%20foreign-linked%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20not%20US%20companies.%20A%20notable%20example%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-the-companies-that-have-cut-ties-with-huawei-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHuawei%2C%20the%20Chinese%20telecoms%20giant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202019.%20Within%20a%20month%20of%20the%20blacklisting%2C%20major%20companies%20like%20Google%20and%20Qualcomm%20severed%20business%20ties%20with%20Huawei.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20the%20stakes%20for%20Anthropic%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20Anthropic%20could%20be%20quasi-nationalized%2C%20or%20they%20could%20be%20driven%20out%20of%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Ball%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20stakes%20are%20huge%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20for%20the%20Defense%20Department%20is%20smaller%20%E2%80%94%20the%20agency%20could%20simply%20walk%20away%20and%20turn%20to%20another%20AI%20company%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20move%20against%20Anthropic%20could%20send%20a%20chilling%20message%20to%20other%20US%20entrepreneurs%2C%20Ball%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20sending%20a%20message%20to%20firms%20that%20doing%20business%20with%20the%20United%20States%20government%20is%20extremely%20dangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20huge%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-department-of-war-pete-hegseth-military-contract-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772103781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e3acc1fb3fcb42648643c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-department-of-war-pete-hegseth-military-contract-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20getting%20blacklisted%20by%20the%20US%20government%20on%20Friday%20unless%20it%20agrees%20to%20terms%20established%20by%20the%20Defense%20Department.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-department-of-war-pete-hegseth-military-contract-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bille%20August%20Sets%20Julius%20Caesar%20TV%20Series%20After%20Scoring%20Global%20Hit%20With%20%E2%80%98Count%20of%20Monte%20Cristo%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772103631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236673283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oscar-winning%20director%20Bille%20August%2C%20who%20recently%20scored%20a%20global%20hit%20with%20TV%20series%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Count%20of%20Monte%20Cristo%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20set%20for%20another%20high-end%20period%20show%20that%20this%20time%20will%20hark%20back%20to%20Ancient%20Rome%20and%20delve%20into%20the%20timely%20figure%20of%20Julius%20Caesar.%20Underlining%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccontemporary%E2%80%9D%20relevance%2C%20August%2C%20in%20an%20exclusive%20statement%20for%20Variety%2C%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nvivarelli%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tattvam%20AI%20raises%20%241.7%20million%20to%20speed%20up%20semiconductor%20chip%20design%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772103218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-02%2F26%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1772102006-8823.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Ftattvam-ai-raise