NY%20WALLACE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJack%20Clark%2C%20an%20Anthropic%20cofounder%2C%20said%20he%20doesn't%20allow%20his%20toddler%20%26quot%3Bunfettered%26quot%3B%20YouTube%20access.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EClark's%20is%20influenced%20by%20his%20dad%20%E2%80%94%20he%20stepped%20in%20when%20Clark%20was%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20weird%26quot%3B%20from%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20isn't%20alone.%20Steve%20Jobs%20and%20Peter%20Thiel%20also%20discussed%20limiting%20their%20children's%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Clark%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-jack-clark-anthropic-ai-billionaire-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20head%20of%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20he%20spends%20his%20days%20thinking%20about%20AI%20guardrails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20he%20says%20he's%20building%20guardrails%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20for%20his%20own%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F02%2F24%2Fopinion%2Fezra-klein-podcast-jack-clark.html%3Fsmid%3Dnytcore-ios-share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ezra%20Klein%20Show%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Clark%20said%20he%20limits%20how%20much%20technology%20his%20toddler%20uses%20and%20is%20uneasy%20about%20algorithmic%20exposure%20for%20his%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20classic%20Californian%20technology%20executive%20view%20of%20not%20having%20that%20much%20technology%20around%20for%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%2C%20who%20recently%20returned%20from%20parental%20leave%20and%20has%20a%20newborn%20at%20home%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20finding%20a%20way%20to%20budget%20your%20child's%20time%20with%20technology%20has%20always%20been%20the%20work%20of%20parents%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20technology%20is%20becoming%20more%20%26quot%3Bubiquitous%2C%26quot%3B%20making%20it%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20escape%26quot%3B%20for%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20Clark%20said%20his%20toddler%20can%20watch%20%26quot%3BBluey%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20few%20other%20shows%20on%20their%20smart%20TV%2C%20but%20he%20hasn't%20allowed%20%26quot%3Bunfettered%20access%20to%20the%20YouTube%20algorithm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20freaks%20me%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark's%20approach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-ceo-parenting-advice-screen-time-chores-for-kids-2024-8%23sundar-pichai-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eechoes%20other%20tech%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20limit%20their%20kids'%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20Miranda%20Kerr%20said%20she%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Snap%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevan-spiegel-ceo-co-founder-snap-life-career%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEvan%20Spiegel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20didn't%20allow%20her%20then-14-year-old%20son%20to%20have%20phones%20or%20computers%20in%20his%20bedroom%20after%209%3A30%20pm.%20In%202024%2C%20PayPal%20cofounder%20Peter%20Thiel%20said%20he%20limits%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-kids-screen-time-parenting-social-media-meta-tech-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echildren's%20screen%20time%20to%2090%20minutes%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20week.%20Apple's%20cofounder%20Steve%20Jobs%20famously%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F09%2F11%2Ffashion%2Fsteve-jobs-apple-was-a-low-tech-parent.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520Walter%2520Isaacson%252C%2520the%2520author%2520of%2Cthe%2520kids%2520didn%2527t%2520seem%2520addicted%2520to%2520devices.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010%20that%20his%20kids%20hadn't%20used%20an%20iPad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20limit%20how%20much%20technology%20our%20kids%20use%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Jobs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20says%20his%20parenting%20model%20is%20partially%20based%20on%20how%20he%20grew%20up.%20His%20father%2C%20who%20had%20a%20computer%20at%20his%20office%2C%20would%20let%20Clark%20use%20the%20machine%20%E2%80%94%20but%20would%20step%20in%20when%20screen%20time%20got%20excessive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20dad%20would%20let%20me%20play%20on%20the%20computer%2C%20and%20at%20some%20point%20he'd%20say%3A%20Jack%2C%20you've%20had%20enough%20computers%20today.%20You're%20getting%20weird%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20systems%20will%20need%20stronger%20parental%20controls%2C%20Clark%20said.%20Those%20guardrails%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20take%20on%20increased%20importance%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20as%20children%20try%20to%20access%20systems%20intended%20for%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20build%20pretty%20heavy%20parental%20controls%20into%20this%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20serve%20ages%2018%20and%20up%20today%2C%20but%20obviously%2C%20kids%20are%20smart%2C%20and%20they're%20going%20to%20try%20to%20get%20onto%20this%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20and%20Anthropic%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20When%20reached%20for%20comment%2C%20a%20YouTube%20spokesperson%20pointed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20guide%20on%20the%20platform's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.youtube%2Finside-youtube%2Fa-decade-of-building-for-teens-and-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20age-appropriate%20experiences%20and%20parental%20controls.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-executive-childs-youtube-freaks-out-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772102641000%2C%22visual%2