0from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20retorting%20technology%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20which%20involves%20heat-treating%20food%20in%20airtight%20containers%20to%20extend%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adapting%20this%20innovative%20approach%2C%20he%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20process%20and%20store%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20room%20temperature%2C%20enhancing%20their%20shelf%20life%20and%20market%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20into%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Brijith%20started%20his%20own%20startup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20raw%20sprouts%2C%20pickles%20to%20manchurian%2C%20soup%20premix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20initial%20challenges%20that%20Brijith%20tackled%20was%20the%20limited%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20their%20seasonal%20nature%2C%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20matured%20cashews%20was%20only%2090%20days.%20Therefore%2C%20year%20round%20availability%20was%20a%20big%20concern.%20Through%20persistent%20research%2C%20trials%2C%20and%20development%20efforts%2C%20I%20successfully%20extended%20the%20germination%20potential%20to%20180-200%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20Brijith%20secured%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20central%20government%20under%20the%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20scheme%20that%20aims%20at%20promoting%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship.%20This%20helped%20him%20kickstart%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20foccussed%20on%20improving%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20in%20order%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%2